,&quot;height&quot;:1226,&quot;width&quot;:1178,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:96732,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/heic&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7c8a1a50-b71a-4527-9224-b1683364ad4d_1178x1226.heic 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7c8a1a50-b71a-4527-9224-b1683364ad4d_1178x1226.heic 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7c8a1a50-b71a-4527-9224-b1683364ad4d_1178x1226.heic 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7c8a1a50-b71a-4527-9224-b1683364ad4d_1178x1226.heic 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">500 der autor Up Luina</figcaption></figure></div><p>Dirbu naktimis, nes tada niekas nelenda. Nes negali bti nieko baisiau kai sau ramiai skrolini feisbuke ir kas nors skambina darbo reikalais:</p><p> Klausau.</p><p> ia dl to stendapo. Turjote praeit savait pasirodyti, o dar nepasirodote.</p><p> inokit, a vis dar labai usims.</p><p> Bet mes ia su mone jau antra savait laukiame.</p><p> Priminkite, kur ir kiek laiko js mans laukiate?</p><p> Bir akt sal. Treia savait. </p><p> Bet ia juk viena geriausi akt sali. Laukiamajame net karto okolado yra. Dabar negaliu. Gal kit savait.</p><p> Tai mums dar ir kit savait imti neapmokam atostog?</p><p> Taip, jei nenorite pravaikt.</p><p>Trumpi skambuiai, bet vis tiek imua i vi. Todl danai sdiu skrolinu nakt. Taip buvo ir praeit nakt skrolinu. Ir girdiu kakas traka. Atsisuku. Aiku u nugaro nieko nra. Bet ir garsas nutyla. Toliau skrolinu. Ir vl girdiu, toks lyg tarkjimas. Kur laik mintis, kad ia mano biologinis laikrodis taip nuo bgimo idivo ir tiksi. Vos nepradjau gglinti how to oil your biological clock.</p><p>Vl iriu u nugaros. Ten vienintelis galimas garso altinis  gl. Prie akis pradeda bgti tie visi timelepsai, kur pagreitintai auga gls. Pradjau galvoti, kad girdiu kaip auga gl. Kyla unikali mintis  rayti gls augimo gars. Bet vos prieinu prie tos gls ji lyg ir nutyla. Pradjau galvoti gal a glei vies ustoju ir ji nebegali augti. Bet kokia viesa nakt? Ir netyia mano vilgsnis nukrypsta  malkas alia idinio. Ir suvokiu, kad tas garsas sklinda, greiiausiai, i malkuose esani kirvarp. </p><p>Tada pradedu galvoti, kad tie vargai Bir akt salje tarka kaip tos kirvapos. Trina sals kdes, parket, dvi vandentiekio sistem. Bir akt sal yra kaip negalintis apsiginti medio gabalas, taromas kirvarp. Net baisu sivaizduoti, koki nuobodybi turi klausytis akt sals sienos. Nedelsiant skambinu  Birus:</p><p> Alio. apsimiegojs balsas.</p><p> Ruokits stendapui. Tuoj bsiu.</p><p>ia naujas klumpi video. Iki bgimo liko maiau nei dvi savaits:</p><div id="youtube2-8O3ozQ0k6TI" class="youtube-wrap" data-attrs="{&quot;videoId&quot;:&quot;8O3ozQ0k6TI&quot;,&quot;startTime&quot;:null,&quot;endTime&quot;:null}" data-component-name="Youtube2ToDOM"><div class="youtube-inner"><iframe src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/8O3ozQ0k6TI?rel=0&amp;autoplay=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;enablejsapi=0" frameborder="0" loading="lazy" gesture="media" allow="autoplay; fullscreen" allowautoplay="true" allowfullscreen="true" width="728" height="409"></iframe></div></div><p>O ia dar keletas trump istorij:</p><p>Neinau ar teisinga nuteisti mones, iimant vien negra segment i j gyvenimo. Sprsti jums. Vakar nakt maiau kaip mano kaimynas, lkdamas su maina, aptak du praeivius. Labai sunervino. Prijau prie t dviej bi. Baiss tokie. Pasakiau, kad inau, kur jo maina stovi. Pasiliau. Visikai ant bajerio. Palaukti ir su raktu subraiyti. Ant bajerio. O tie rimtai prim. Taip entuziastingai, kad a jau negaljau gaidintis ir neberodyti mainos. Nueinam  mano kiem. Matom main. Tie pradeda mtytis. A vl ant bajerio jiems pasakau, kad jau tamsu ir kamer pas mus nra. Isitraukiam raktus. A tai ant bajerio. Nesitikjau, kad tie braiys. Jiems braiant, o man tupint i kitos puss. Maina atsirakina ir usidega viesos. Kaimynas kak paliko mainoje. Tie bgti prie vart. Vargai nerado mygtuko. Main su raktu braiyti nagli, bet kai reikia galv naudoti, nebeieina. Kaimynas ikviet policij. A, prisidengs tamsa, slikinau  savo laiptin. Grau pasimets. Nuslikindamas girdjau kaip jie visi trys graiai kalbjosi. Tipo visi nekalti. Avinliai. Nors gal be reikalo a juos teisiu. Nors mans tai jau nelieia, dabar greitai temsta, rekomenduoju usidti atvaist, kad kaimynas laiku pamatyt ir nereikt staigiai  balas sukti ir taip aptakyti kitus mones.</p><p>***</p><p>Traukiny moteris per telefon klausosi muzikos. Prieais sdintis vyras, mandagiai pasilo paskolinti ausines. Moteris nesupranta. Atsako, kad ausini nenaudoja. Mes visi girdime, kad nenaudojate. Bet kodl nenaudojate? ypsosi vyras. Nes jeigu it din muzik pasileisiau per ausines man pradt kraujuoti aus bugneliai. Tai, kodl jos klausots? Man feisbukas nesilo kitos. Vyras atsistoja ir surkia. Mes visi galime jums padti! Ar ne taip? Troleibuse kyla sambrzdis. Dabar taip. A paimu i itos moters telefon, o js jos feisbuke palaikinate savo mgstam atlikj. Moteris kak bando sakyti. Nusiraminkite. A profesionalas. Mes sugriausime js algoritmus. Po deimties minui troleibuse tyla. Moteris klausosi muzikos su ausinmis. Prie vyro prieina kitas vyrikis:</p><p> O gal inote, kaip ant dujins nustatyti laikrod? Niekaip nepavyksta.</p><p>***</p><p>Apsipirkinju savitarnoje. Girdiu kaip apsauginis rkia ant paauglio. Kiek tu ia laiko stovsi? Krauk greiiau savo tuos ipsus ir eik lauk. Nesikiu. A internete sskaitas suvedinju. Vieni kvieia  lauk ieiti pakalbti. A kvieiu  internet. Ateisi  internet  tau aks. Penkias valandas tavo laiko sudauysiu kaip uog. Komentarai yra mano ringas. Laiko nokdaunas. Supratot. Paauglys kak pabamba ir ieina. Pairiu  apsaugin ir suprantu, kad nra ans, kad jis ateis pas mane  komentarus. Nusprendiu pasiteirauti. Atsipraau, o kiek laiko turiu prie savitarnos? ypsosi jis man. Taigi suaugs mogus esi. Nesupratau, o k tai bendro turi stovjimu prie kasos? Dabar juk prakaitavimo metas. Nesvarbu ar su striuke ar su megztiniu ieisi  lauka  suprakaituosi. Tie paaugliai i mokyklos atbga  parduotuv ir dar labiau suprakaitav ibga  lauk. Ir paskui perla. Snargliuojasi. Bandiau jiems draugikai paaikinti. Be ans. Tai reikia parkti. Ijau nieko nepasaks. Tik namie atsidars feisbuk prie draug pasilym radau apsaugin. Nekviesiu. Tegul saugo paauglius. Linkiu nesusirgti.</p></body></html>	Naktinis darbas be trikdi. Netikti darbo skambuiai trukdo scroll'inti. Paslaptingi nakties garsai nuveda iki juoking suvokim apie auganius augalus ir mlavabalius. Spontanikas sprendimas daryti stand-up Biruose.	2024-10-08 06:04:52	2024-10-08 12:03:29.059	2024-10-08 15:33:44.503	{lithuanian}	https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7c8a1a50-b71a-4527-9224-b1683364ad4d_1178x1226.heic	Domas Raibys	u-k-balsuoti
3	https://timdenning.substack.com/p/the-greatest-book-on-money-ive-read	The Greatest Book on Money Ive Read In The Last 24 Months	Bizarrely, the book title has nothing to do with money	<div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7a62ba7c-a1a4-4029-9e79-977f305a7134_1166x695.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7a62ba7c-a1a4-4029-9e79-977f305a7134_1166x695.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7a62ba7c-a1a4-4029-9e79-977f305a7134_1166x695.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7a62ba7c-a1a4-4029-9e79-977f305a7134_1166x695.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7a62ba7c-a1a4-4029-9e79-977f305a7134_1166x695.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7a62ba7c-a1a4-4029-9e79-977f305a7134_1166x695.jpeg" width="1166" height="695" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/7a62ba7c-a1a4-4029-9e79-977f305a7134_1166x695.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:695,&quot;width&quot;:1166,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:172865,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7a62ba7c-a1a4-4029-9e79-977f305a7134_1166x695.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7a62ba7c-a1a4-4029-9e79-977f305a7134_1166x695.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7a62ba7c-a1a4-4029-9e79-977f305a7134_1166x695.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7a62ba7c-a1a4-4029-9e79-977f305a7134_1166x695.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption"><em>Image Credit-Midjourney</em></figcaption></figure></div><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://timdenning.substack.com/p/the-greatest-book-on-money-ive-read?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Share&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"><a class="button primary" href="https://timdenning.substack.com/p/the-greatest-book-on-money-ive-read?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share"><span>Share</span></a></p><p>Finance nerds ruined books on money.</p><p>Technical jargon. Graphs. Lambo photos. Banking stories. Such a huge snoozer. Whenever people ask me what books to read about money it&#8217;s hard. But one book I read in the last 24 months blew my mind:</p><p><em>&#8220;How To Live&#8221;</em> by Derek Sivers. It doesn&#8217;t seem like a book about money but it is.</p><p>Here&#8217;s what you can learn from it.</p><h1><strong>The biggest money lesson from </strong><em>&#8220;How To Live&#8221;</em></h1><p>I always hated when people made lots of money.</p><p>I loved to throw mud at billionaires while sipping a one-dollar 7-Eleven coffee. Then Derek Sivers said this:</p><blockquote><p><em>"Making money is nothing more than a neutral exchange of value. Making money is proof you're adding value to people's lives. Aiming to get rich is aiming to be useful to the world."</em></p></blockquote><p>Making money is helping people.</p><p>When someone makes a lot of money it means they&#8217;ve helped a lot of people, and you should at least shake their hand. You should probably also try to learn something from them. Only closed-minded losers shame wealthy people.</p><div class="pullquote"><p>"Making money isn't evil, greedy, shallow, or vain. Your biggest obstacle to getting rich is the harmful meaning you've attached to it."</p></div><h1>Money doesn&#8217;t give a f*ck about these things&#8230;</h1><blockquote><p><em>"Money doesn't care about your:</em></p><p><em>&#8226; Race</em></p><p><em>&#8226; Gender</em></p><p><em>&#8226; Education</em></p><p><em>&#8226; Physique</em></p><p><em>&#8226; Family</em></p><p><em>&#8226; Nationality</em></p><p><em>Anyone can be rich &#8211; so it might as well be you."</em></p></blockquote><p>I suspect this one will blow up a few people&#8217;s brains.</p><p>We&#8217;re taught by society to be victims. To blame our money problems on a 3rd party or even politicians. But no president is going to save you or your bank account. They&#8217;re busy building theirs and enjoying their newfound status.</p><p>One of my good friends makes 7-figures (USD) a year. He comes from a poor village in Africa. He decided to change his family&#8217;s future.</p><p>The only thing stopping you getting wealthy are your bullsh*t excuses about why it can&#8217;t happen. Money has nothing to do with IQ, and everything to do with helpfulness.</p><h1>&#8220;If more information was the answer, we'd all be billionaires with perfect abs.&#8221;</h1><p>Most people drown in information. They think the information age is the future.</p><p>Wrong. It&#8217;s the past. AI screwed the information age in the butt. We&#8217;re now drowning in information. Amazon is filled with AI-written books. Social media has AI sludge all over it. Our email inboxes are the next target for AI.</p><p>What a lot of people are missing is more action.</p><p>Taking what you&#8217;ve already learned and putting it to good use. Consuming more information is often nothing more than procrastination in disguise. It&#8217;s why my academy now offers execution instead of information.</p><p>Get around other people with the same goal. Take daily action.</p><h1>"Ideas are worth almost nothing.</h1><h1>Execution is everything. The world is filled with ideas, yet so few take action and make them happen."</h1><p>I met someone recently who had an idea for an AI marketplace.</p><p>They didn&#8217;t want to talk about it. They wanted me to sign an NDA. I told them &#8220;no one gives a f*ck about another AI chatbot idea. There&#8217;s nothing unique here, just like Uber but for boats isn&#8217;t a genius idea (a bank customer once wanted me to sign an NDA over this idea, too&#8230;LOL).</p><p>Investors and banks don&#8217;t invest in ideas. They invest in execution.</p><p>Do you have any results? Do you have customers? Have you earned any money from it? That&#8217;s the hard part.</p><p>We don&#8217;t value Elon Musk because he had a great idea of sending rockets to Mars. We value him because he sent rockets to space and saved real astronauts who were stranded.</p><p>Become an action-taker to get wealthy. Throw your ideas in the bin. What I learned is that dumb ideas often make the most money &#8211; life is a paradox.</p><h1>&#8220;The purpose of <strong>money</strong> is to trade for things that make you happy.</h1><h1>So if you can bypass <strong>money</strong> and get directly to the happy, you've saved a lot of trouble.&#8221;</h1><p>Not needing stuff is a huge money hack.</p><p>My Honda Civic is 9 years old. She still drives like a dream. I could easily replace it with a Lambo 4WD tomorrow. Yet I don&#8217;t. I don&#8217;t need another car. I have zero desire for material possessions or status. So I don&#8217;t need to earn as much money to live, which means my freedom number is 10x lower than the average person.</p><p>It also means I can retire decades earlier than most corporate rats.</p><p>What I chase is happiness. My 1 year old daughter gives me all of that for the cost of new nappies and some Bluey books with the occasional cafe smoothie.</p><p>Money can make your life complicated or simple. Choose simple.</p><h1><strong>&#8220;We do so many things for money whether we need it or not&#8221;</strong></h1><p>The virtue-signalling unicorns in the West love to pretend they don&#8217;t work for money.</p><p>They think they&#8217;re too good for money. They&#8217;re special. They&#8217;re driven by purpose. They&#8217;re writing the novel for the love of it. They would never dare &#8216;monetize&#8217; a hobby. How dare you!</p><p>I call bullsh*t.</p><p>We do things for money even if we don&#8217;t need money. Getting paid helps us feel like we&#8217;re not being exploited. Better yet&#8230;</p><pre><code>Money helps make our work better.</code></pre><p>When you get paid you can build a website, hire a virtual assistant, get a fancy book cover designed by a cartoonist, and buy software to make your productivity higher.</p><p>Never trust a person who says they don&#8217;t need money.</p><h1>"Making money is a skill. Learn it and practice it like you would any other."</h1><p>Some people spend their entire lives struggling with money.</p><p>I was that person too. What changed for me was when I realized making money is a skill. There&#8217;s an art to crafting offers, sending proposals, pricing your time, and gently persuading someone to get your help.</p><p>Instead of treating money as this mysterious thing you never have enough of, turn it into an art form with a set of skills attached that you can learn.</p><h1>"Don't buy too many things, too big of a house, or hire too many people.</h1><h1>Rich people who do this feel trapped and miserable. The less you buy, the more you're in control."</h1><p>As your wealth increases it&#8217;s tempting to buy more stuff.</p><p>I&#8217;m a fan of hiring people to get more of your time back and build leverage, but there&#8217;s a threshold where a team of people can become a huge burden.</p><p>Material possessions require maintenance. That needs more money. And every item occupies some mental bandwidth.</p><p>The less stuff you own, the less your stuff owns you.</p><h1>"The more something costs, the more people value it.</h1><h1>By charging more, you're actually helping them use it and appreciate it."</h1><p>How you price your products and services is psychological, too.</p><p>Some people accidentally accept a low salary because they don&#8217;t know their own value. They think they have to be the lowest-cost option to get the job.</p><p>What I found when I applied for new jobs is the higher I told them my expected salary was the more seriously they wanted to hire me. A $300K a year salesperson sounds like they&#8217;d be better than a $50K a year one.</p><p>The same applies to business. I ran a $10K service and felt guilty for the high price tag. But the customers loved it because the cost forced them to take action and get results in 30 days.</p><div class="pullquote"><p>"Charge more than is comfortable to your current self-image. Value yourself higher, then rise to fit this valuation."</p></div><h1>"To get rich, don't think about what's valuable to you. Think about what's valuable to others."</h1><p>Selfish people are broke.</p><p>When it comes to making money they always think about their selfish desires and wants. They never think about how they can be helpful. This selfishness is a disease. It comes from the current <em>me, me, me</em> culture.</p><pre><code>Harsh truth: nobody gives a f*ck about you and what you want in life.</code></pre><p>We&#8217;re all thinking about ourselves. So put others ahead and you&#8217;ll be an uncommon mofo who&#8217;ll make more money than feels humanly possible. I never try to guess what is valuable in my business. I ask people. I survey them. I have Zoom calls with them.</p><p>Selflessness will make you wealthy.</p><h1>&#8220;Emotions are the enemy of good investing."</h1><p>The dumbest people I&#8217;ve ever met are day traders.</p><p>They don&#8217;t understand that it&#8217;s just gambling with a s*xier label. They often trade stocks, FX or crypto and even do courses to learn this magical skill.</p><p>Anyone who has worked in finance knows that buying &amp; selling any investment in the short term is gambling.</p><p>What screws day traders are their emotions.</p><p>It&#8217;s a constant high and low rollercoaster. Ultimately they lose every dollar&#8230; or they win the jackpot by accident and gamble it all back. Stay away from emotion-driven, short-term investing.</p><h1>&#8220;The world is full of money. There's no shortage. So capture the value you create. Charge for what you do."</h1><p>Money used to be scarce.</p><p>You were born in a country and the opportunities there defined your financial potential. If you grew up in a poor place you had to migrate to somewhere like America. It was complicated, expensive, and came with a waiting list.</p><p>Since the internet took over the planet everything has changed. It&#8217;s a borderless, global marketplace that&#8217;s open 24/7. We&#8217;re no longer limited by anything. And there are billions of dollars on the internet every day that are accessible to you.</p><p>The only limitation is whether you can attract that money to your life. That starts with ethically gaining some attention on social media, and choosing a half-decent business model.</p><p>The last one is key. Many people choose Uber slave driver income streams, like freelancing marketplaces, then wonder why their life turns to cr*ap.</p><p>Gain attention. Choose a digital income stream that&#8217;s proven to make cash. Then tell your old 9-5 boss to stick their job where the sun don&#8217;t shine (proud to have done this).</p><h1>"The world needs more boldness.</h1><h1>Refuse the comfortable addiction of a steady paycheck."</h1><p>The comfortable life is a nightmare.</p><p>It leads to mediocrity that pays the worst. You face high competition and the constant threat of the layoff boogie monster that&#8217;ll bite your titties off.</p><p>I have no problem with people starting with a paycheck. What&#8217;s sad is when it ends there. The bold thing to do is go out on your own and have multiple employers (customers). It forces you to stay sharp and add value. You can&#8217;t get lost in a big organization or hide behind a department for cover and free pizza.</p><p>Since I quit my job in 2021 my skills have increased by at least 100x. I&#8217;ve spent wild amounts of money on coaching, masterminds, courses, and events that have helped me gain new micro skills.</p><p>In banking, my only skill was order-taking (sales) and perhaps sending a few emails to customers with transaction fees on them.</p><p>Choose the path of growth and discomfort if you want to be wealthy.</p><h1>"Nothing destroys money faster than seeking status."</h1><p>I met a guy a few months back. Nice fellow. I wrote about him in another Substack.</p><p>He bought a BMW. He felt incredible. But the status cost him $3000 a month plus 15% a year in interest on the loan. If he invested that money in a business he would probably have quit his job by now.</p><p>When he handed over the cash to the German car company, everything at work was great. Now it isn&#8217;t. A new boss started. They micro-manage him. They took away his 6-figure bonus. Chasing status is stupid. The richest people look ordinary.</p><p>Real status is the free time to do whatever the F you want.</p><h1><strong>Closing Thought</strong></h1><p>I strongly recommend you read &#8220;How To Live.&#8221; It will change your financial life.</p><p>What&#8217;s your favorite money idea above from Derek?</p><p><em>This article is for informational purposes only, it should not be considered financial, tax or legal advice. Consult a financial professional before making any major financial decisions.</em></p><div><hr></div><p>P.S. Reading about money is nice.&nbsp;</p><p>Writing to make money is even better.&nbsp;</p><p>I can show you how in next week's free masterclass</p><p><a href="https://event.webinarjam.com/register/69/gp84gs6w">Click here to reserve your seat now</a></p><p>(Limited seating)</p>	Money isn't evil - it's proof you're adding value. Anyone can be rich, regardless of background. Focus on execution, not just ideas. Simplify your life to need less. Treat making money as a skill to learn. Price yourself higher to be valued more.	2024-10-03 11:04:07	2024-10-05 19:39:31.379	2024-10-07 16:00:37.892	{english}	https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7a62ba7c-a1a4-4029-9e79-977f305a7134_1166x695.jpeg	Tim Denning	the-greatest-book-on-money-ive-read-in-the-last-24-months
14	https://niallharbison.substack.com/p/creating-a-global-movement	Creating A Global Movement	So many people now involved	<p>Most people reading this will probably know I started this mission in 2022 by feeding a single street dog myself. Her name was Lucky and <a href="https://niallharbison.substack.com/p/lucky">you can read her story here</a>. </p><p>From that single dog has grown a movement of epic proportions and I wanted to try showcase just how many people are involved and how much change is happening.</p><p>I have to pinch myself that these numbers are real&#8230; </p><h3>25,000 Dogs Sterilised</h3><p>Just this week we sterilised the <a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_7U1w7SlLS/">25,000th dog</a>. Fittingly it was one here on the island of Koh Samui where it all started. Some of the stats around our sterilising (it means to neuter or spay) are beyond exciting&#8230;</p><ul><li><p>We now have <a href="https://www.happydoggo.com/our-work">8 partners in 3 countries</a> (Thailand, Sri Lanka and Indonesia)</p></li><li><p>We are now funding the sterilising of around 5000 dogs per month</p></li><li><p>Sterilising 25,000 dogs means we have stopped <strong>a quarter of a million</strong> puppies being born into suffering (counting on approx 10 puppies per dog)</p></li></ul><p>The plans to ramp this up for the rest of this year and especially into 2025 are even more ambitious. </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59e8da2e-a312-41b6-a6a3-65025447800a_1600x900.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59e8da2e-a312-41b6-a6a3-65025447800a_1600x900.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59e8da2e-a312-41b6-a6a3-65025447800a_1600x900.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59e8da2e-a312-41b6-a6a3-65025447800a_1600x900.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59e8da2e-a312-41b6-a6a3-65025447800a_1600x900.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59e8da2e-a312-41b6-a6a3-65025447800a_1600x900.png" width="1456" height="819" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/59e8da2e-a312-41b6-a6a3-65025447800a_1600x900.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:819,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:202986,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59e8da2e-a312-41b6-a6a3-65025447800a_1600x900.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59e8da2e-a312-41b6-a6a3-65025447800a_1600x900.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59e8da2e-a312-41b6-a6a3-65025447800a_1600x900.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59e8da2e-a312-41b6-a6a3-65025447800a_1600x900.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><p>While we build the partnerships and provide the funding there are close to 100 people out there on the ground doing the hard work of catching, operating on and safely returning the dogs to their communities. They are the true heroes.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3315e537-ffc2-43a9-95cf-dc51d2aae75c_1162x726.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3315e537-ffc2-43a9-95cf-dc51d2aae75c_1162x726.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3315e537-ffc2-43a9-95cf-dc51d2aae75c_1162x726.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3315e537-ffc2-43a9-95cf-dc51d2aae75c_1162x726.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3315e537-ffc2-43a9-95cf-dc51d2aae75c_1162x726.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3315e537-ffc2-43a9-95cf-dc51d2aae75c_1162x726.png" width="1162" height="726" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/3315e537-ffc2-43a9-95cf-dc51d2aae75c_1162x726.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:726,&quot;width&quot;:1162,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:1841432,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3315e537-ffc2-43a9-95cf-dc51d2aae75c_1162x726.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3315e537-ffc2-43a9-95cf-dc51d2aae75c_1162x726.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3315e537-ffc2-43a9-95cf-dc51d2aae75c_1162x726.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3315e537-ffc2-43a9-95cf-dc51d2aae75c_1162x726.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><h3>Dogs Number 26, 27 &amp; 28 - Billy Rusty And Sandy</h3><p>While the huge numbers are so compelling I find the individual dogs are the ones that really melt my heart. In 2024 alone we have now re-homed 28 dogs both in Thailand and around the world. </p><ul><li><p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/best_boy_billy">Billy</a>. He arrived in Singapore after his horrific slashing.</p></li><li><p><a href="https://x.com/NiallHarbison/status/1835351206337888663">Sandy and Rusty</a> Both found suffering but now snuggled up in England</p></li></ul><p>It&#8217;s really hard to explain just how many people are involved in getting them to their homes. The wonderful kind people who adopt these dogs and all the care they get during their rescues. For a dog like Billy I am not exaggerating when I say there are up to 50 people who helped him at various stages. </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd3df3e4d-7a46-465a-9868-6abc25b3dd0a_1332x634.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd3df3e4d-7a46-465a-9868-6abc25b3dd0a_1332x634.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd3df3e4d-7a46-465a-9868-6abc25b3dd0a_1332x634.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd3df3e4d-7a46-465a-9868-6abc25b3dd0a_1332x634.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd3df3e4d-7a46-465a-9868-6abc25b3dd0a_1332x634.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd3df3e4d-7a46-465a-9868-6abc25b3dd0a_1332x634.png" width="1332" height="634" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/d3df3e4d-7a46-465a-9868-6abc25b3dd0a_1332x634.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:634,&quot;width&quot;:1332,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:1718755,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd3df3e4d-7a46-465a-9868-6abc25b3dd0a_1332x634.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd3df3e4d-7a46-465a-9868-6abc25b3dd0a_1332x634.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd3df3e4d-7a46-465a-9868-6abc25b3dd0a_1332x634.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd3df3e4d-7a46-465a-9868-6abc25b3dd0a_1332x634.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><h3>Building Out A Thai Team</h3><p>I&#8217;m very conscious of the fact that I am in Thailand and we are never going to solve the dog problem here with foreign staff alone. <a href="https://www.happydoggo.com/">Happy Doggo</a> needs to be led by local people in the countries it operates in and integrate into the community. That process has started. Seeing our team in our new offices with the logo on the wall makes me so proud. </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F668eaf81-deae-4ac2-aaa5-4852b3cac81c_2048x1536.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F668eaf81-deae-4ac2-aaa5-4852b3cac81c_2048x1536.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F668eaf81-deae-4ac2-aaa5-4852b3cac81c_2048x1536.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F668eaf81-deae-4ac2-aaa5-4852b3cac81c_2048x1536.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F668eaf81-deae-4ac2-aaa5-4852b3cac81c_2048x1536.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F668eaf81-deae-4ac2-aaa5-4852b3cac81c_2048x1536.jpeg" width="1456" height="1092" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/668eaf81-deae-4ac2-aaa5-4852b3cac81c_2048x1536.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1092,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:270223,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F668eaf81-deae-4ac2-aaa5-4852b3cac81c_2048x1536.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F668eaf81-deae-4ac2-aaa5-4852b3cac81c_2048x1536.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F668eaf81-deae-4ac2-aaa5-4852b3cac81c_2048x1536.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F668eaf81-deae-4ac2-aaa5-4852b3cac81c_2048x1536.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><p>The following slide is from one of our internal decks. You can see just how fast we are trying to scale up. Most of these people will be rolling our sterilising and local operations to help more dogs on the ground as quickly as we possibly can. </p><p>You are probably as blown away by the scale of the growth as I am nervous about how to fund it all and the logistics involved. Luckily there are some outstanding people working on this behind the scenes. </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F65468ca7-8b58-4fe2-ad4a-9b099b01d455_1594x896.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F65468ca7-8b58-4fe2-ad4a-9b099b01d455_1594x896.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F65468ca7-8b58-4fe2-ad4a-9b099b01d455_1594x896.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F65468ca7-8b58-4fe2-ad4a-9b099b01d455_1594x896.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F65468ca7-8b58-4fe2-ad4a-9b099b01d455_1594x896.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F65468ca7-8b58-4fe2-ad4a-9b099b01d455_1594x896.png" width="1456" height="818" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/65468ca7-8b58-4fe2-ad4a-9b099b01d455_1594x896.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:818,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:434711,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F65468ca7-8b58-4fe2-ad4a-9b099b01d455_1594x896.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F65468ca7-8b58-4fe2-ad4a-9b099b01d455_1594x896.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F65468ca7-8b58-4fe2-ad4a-9b099b01d455_1594x896.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F65468ca7-8b58-4fe2-ad4a-9b099b01d455_1594x896.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><h3>Local Support For Tina&#8217;s Hospital </h3><p>The work is really ramping up on <a href="https://www.happydoggo.com/tinas-hospital">Tina&#8217;s Hospital</a>. Not just from a design perspective with our wonderful <a href="https://www.happydoggo.com/tinas-hospital">pro bono partners</a> but also on the ground. </p><p>We had a meeting with the Mayor of Samui last week about building the public road into the hospital for us and the feedback has been excellent. Explaining our big picture thinking and seeing it so well received by key local decision makers was something I&#8217;d long been dreaming of.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3bde1ed0-0f29-4127-96bd-98546f29782d_1344x742.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3bde1ed0-0f29-4127-96bd-98546f29782d_1344x742.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3bde1ed0-0f29-4127-96bd-98546f29782d_1344x742.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3bde1ed0-0f29-4127-96bd-98546f29782d_1344x742.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3bde1ed0-0f29-4127-96bd-98546f29782d_1344x742.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3bde1ed0-0f29-4127-96bd-98546f29782d_1344x742.png" width="1344" height="742" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/3bde1ed0-0f29-4127-96bd-98546f29782d_1344x742.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:742,&quot;width&quot;:1344,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:1819775,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3bde1ed0-0f29-4127-96bd-98546f29782d_1344x742.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3bde1ed0-0f29-4127-96bd-98546f29782d_1344x742.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3bde1ed0-0f29-4127-96bd-98546f29782d_1344x742.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3bde1ed0-0f29-4127-96bd-98546f29782d_1344x742.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><h3>An Online Army Of Dog Lovers</h3><p>If you look through the various areas I&#8217;ve outlined above there are a couple of hundred people already involved in various ways thanks to what has been created at <a href="https://www.happydoggo.com/">Happy Doggo</a>. A lot of dog lovers changing the world. A global movement.</p><p>What makes this work though is the 1000s of other people around the world supporting, sharing content and commenting with kind words and gestures. I feel it every single day and am always taken aback by people&#8217;s generosity in so many ways. </p><p>Like little Eve here and her <a href="https://www.justgiving.com/page/jade-nayyar-1723984325403">story after moving to England</a> and all who supported her recent climb. Thats one of 100 examples I could have picked.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F86198052-8e11-437f-88ff-7e8f1d65cee7_1338x990.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F86198052-8e11-437f-88ff-7e8f1d65cee7_1338x990.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F86198052-8e11-437f-88ff-7e8f1d65cee7_1338x990.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F86198052-8e11-437f-88ff-7e8f1d65cee7_1338x990.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F86198052-8e11-437f-88ff-7e8f1d65cee7_1338x990.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F86198052-8e11-437f-88ff-7e8f1d65cee7_1338x990.png" width="1338" height="990" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/86198052-8e11-437f-88ff-7e8f1d65cee7_1338x990.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:990,&quot;width&quot;:1338,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:2539905,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F86198052-8e11-437f-88ff-7e8f1d65cee7_1338x990.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F86198052-8e11-437f-88ff-7e8f1d65cee7_1338x990.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F86198052-8e11-437f-88ff-7e8f1d65cee7_1338x990.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F86198052-8e11-437f-88ff-7e8f1d65cee7_1338x990.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><p>Things are getting scarily big and very expensive and tricky to run logistically but the support online is the key element. I feel so many people want to help the dogs in any way possible even if they are half way across the world. That support takes my breath away on a daily basis. In a world with so much bad news and dark moments I think this is a little corner of the world that shows positive change can happen.</p><p>I wanted to write this update because I always get outsized credit. In comments, media coverage and in person. As you can clearly see this is a team effort and you reading this are very much part of that. </p><p>All I can do is keep dreaming even bigger and figuring out ways to save even more dogs because they are the ones suffering right now. </p><p>Thank you from the bottom of my heart. </p><p>Big Love</p><p>Niall</p><p>P.S You can always support by either <a href="https://www.happydoggo.com/donate">donating here</a> or just subscribing to this newsletter.</p><h3></h3><p></p>	A movement to help street dogs has grown exponentially, sterilizing 25,000 dogs across three countries. Local teams are expanding rapidly to scale up efforts and build a new hospital, with widespread community support.	2024-09-16 15:17:30	2024-10-05 19:41:03.066	2024-10-07 16:00:38.165	{english}	https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3315e537-ffc2-43a9-95cf-dc51d2aae75c_1162x726.png	Niall Harbison	creating-a-global-movement
83	https://vartotojogidas.substack.com/p/vartotojo-gidas-rugsejui-6bb	VARTOTOJO GIDAS rugsjui	Vartojimas vartojimui nelygus, o dl skonio ginijamasi	<html><head></head><body><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9268610f-60be-4329-be44-6e9a53e03144_2160x1346.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9268610f-60be-4329-be44-6e9a53e03144_2160x1346.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9268610f-60be-4329-be44-6e9a53e03144_2160x1346.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9268610f-60be-4329-be44-6e9a53e03144_2160x1346.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9268610f-60be-4329-be44-6e9a53e03144_2160x1346.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9268610f-60be-4329-be44-6e9a53e03144_2160x1346.png" width="1456" height="907" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/9268610f-60be-4329-be44-6e9a53e03144_2160x1346.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:907,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:3297833,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9268610f-60be-4329-be44-6e9a53e03144_2160x1346.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9268610f-60be-4329-be44-6e9a53e03144_2160x1346.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9268610f-60be-4329-be44-6e9a53e03144_2160x1346.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9268610f-60be-4329-be44-6e9a53e03144_2160x1346.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">Kadras i filmo Karei-naru tsuiseki (Norifumi Suzuki, 1975)<em> </em></figcaption></figure></div><h4><em>Laikratis:</em> Kada paskutin kart pirkote popieri?</h4><p>Nesu tikras, kokia lietuvikos kultrins spaudos funkcija. Susiskaldiusi  atomus, ji danai bando ne auginti, vertinti, provokuoti, o pateisinti savo egzistavim, atidirbti ir sisavinti. Todl turime per daug kultros leidini, per maai skaitytoj ir vidutinik kokyb. Ir tuomet aminas Litmenis susiima ir pasikvieia Le Monde, udraudia sau rayti, iveria pastarj met kelis prancz ilgaskaiius ir itas bendras numeris staiga ugroja. Popierius veikia, kaip internetas neveikt: pateisina sultjim. </p><p>Horizontus pleiantys rainiai apie vilt tragikais laikais, dvi islamo puses, griuvsius kaip atmin, progerija sergani iuolaikin McArchitektr, nesugaudom wokeizm. Viename numeryje! <a href="https://literaturairmenas.lt/zurnalas/3797">Nusipirkite j, gal net du</a>  Literatra ir menas + Le Monde gali bti ir dovana. Sklando faktai, kad jau pus tirao iparduota  nestabdome. </p><div><hr></div><h4><em>Knyga:</em> Benjamin Labatut Kai liaujams suprasti pasaul (Rara, 2022)</h4><p>Umberto Eco mok  reikia turti gerokai daugiau knyg nei gali perskaityti. Kitaip esi tik vartotojas, perdm praktikas. Tad Labatutas vos pasirods smuko  mano lentyn pilv, o atsiveriau tik ukaszo Twarkowskio pakusintas. Jo k tik pasirods spektaklis Quanta, pasirodo, turs daug bendro su ia nefikcins literatros knyga. Mats ir skaits galiu pasakyti: nesutinku. I knygos isineiau visai ne tas temas. Joje sutinkame mokslo haliucinacij parates, kuomet suvokimas kaip viskas veikia ima sprogdinti i vidaus, kai prietaraujanios svokos sugyvena, matematika tampa poezija, fizikoje svarbsta elegantikumas, iradimai naikina ir gelbja monij kone vienu metu, o beprotyb ir atrus protas susikabina rankomis. BL kyteli savo talent iversti ir itransliuoti nepasiekiamus mokslo laiptus  pirmiausiai, mogikj dram. Joje tiek genijams, tiek mirtingiesiems artima abejon, konkurencija, aistra, idealizmas ir velniava. <a href="https://knygynas.biz/products/kai-liaujames-suprasti-pasauli">"Eureka! turi.</a></p><div><hr></div><h4><em>Negroin knyga:</em> Vinciane Despret K atsakyt gyvnai, jei uduotume jiems teisingus klausimus? (Phi, 2023)</h4><p>Filosofo darbas yra nuolatos destabilizuoti: bet juk tai tu gali matyti ir kitaip. Despret tai yra gyvnai ir ji ia apsiginklavusi ne tik skvarbiu kritiniu skalpeliu, bet ir drsiais mokslininkais. Kartu jie vien po kito guldo nepatogius, kreivus, retai uduodamus klausimus. Kas domaus eksperimentuose gyvnams? Ar jie turi humoro jausm? Gal karvs yra autistikos mokslininks? <a href="https://knygynas.biz/products/ka-pasakytu-gyvunai-jei-uzduotume-jiems-teisingus-klausimus">Labai malonus susivlimas.</a></p><div><hr></div><h4><em>Filmas namuose:</em> La Circle Rouge (Jean Pierre Melville, 1970)</h4><p>Soctinkluose k tik nosinmis atmojavome prancz kino ikonai Alainui Delonui. Bet su mirusiais aktoriais reikia atsisveikinti irint j darbus. Galima apie juos pasiskaityti (AD ir ultra-deinys buvo, ir kaljime pasdjo u karo tarnybos vengim, ir su Korsikos mafijos kriktatviu vakarliavo), bet iri film ir viskas aiku, ko jis buvo vertas. Pasirinkau legendinio <em>noir</em> anro augintojo Jeano Pierre Melville ltas, maaemoces, tylias gaudynes Raudonasis ratas. Jame tno ir nuostabi, 27 minutes trunkanti plimo scena be joki odi, cigarete nei burna kalbantis Delono banditlis, siurrealistiniai demon egzorcizmai ir vorikas policijos tinklas. Ai, ir vidurinis pirtas skubiems neftlixo <em>crime </em>serialiukams.</p><div><hr></div><h4><em>Projektas:</em> Pasakykite Anai kokia bus naujien ateitis</h4><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe54a10ab-c863-414a-abba-9ff801179f5e_2551x1402.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe54a10ab-c863-414a-abba-9ff801179f5e_2551x1402.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe54a10ab-c863-414a-abba-9ff801179f5e_2551x1402.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe54a10ab-c863-414a-abba-9ff801179f5e_2551x1402.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe54a10ab-c863-414a-abba-9ff801179f5e_2551x1402.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe54a10ab-c863-414a-abba-9ff801179f5e_2551x1402.jpeg" width="1456" height="800" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/e54a10ab-c863-414a-abba-9ff801179f5e_2551x1402.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:800,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:4018687,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe54a10ab-c863-414a-abba-9ff801179f5e_2551x1402.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe54a10ab-c863-414a-abba-9ff801179f5e_2551x1402.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe54a10ab-c863-414a-abba-9ff801179f5e_2551x1402.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe54a10ab-c863-414a-abba-9ff801179f5e_2551x1402.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><p>Per vasar nelabai degiau, bet kartu su A-komanda ukrme An, naujien asistent, kuri nepailstamai dirba naujien surinkimo, atrinkimo, esms iraymo, personalizavimo darbus. Tam, kad js galtumte susigaudyti pasaulio vykiuose per minut-kit ir nebti siurbti  nesibaigiant naujienyi vorteks.</p><p>Ana dar bandoma, tobulinama, todl ir noriu pakviesti jus padti j testuoti, komentuoti, patarti ir, jei yra u k, pagirti. Krj ausys temptos. Kol kas ji skirta tik <em>iPhone</em> turtojams ir tiems, kas veiks dviej ingsni <em>Apple</em> reikalavimus: <a href="https://testflight.apple.com/join/qMsUhjMb">pirmiausiai atsisis </a><em><a href="https://testflight.apple.com/join/qMsUhjMb">Test Flight</a></em><a href="https://testflight.apple.com/join/qMsUhjMb"> programl, o tada jau sileis ir pai An.</a></p><div><hr></div><h4><em>Instagram:</em> Subway Takes </h4><p>Iduosiu savo irimiausi Instaprojekt. Tai  beveik kasdieniai atsitiktines temas, bet neatsitiktinius personaus sileidiantys Kareem Rahma micro-intervai Niujorke, pavadinti Subway Takes. Formatas paprastas ir todl toks geras: Kareemas pasisodina panekov ir klausia: So, whats your take?. Tada suteikia sekundi savo tezei idstyti, tarkim: mergvakariai yra lamtas, ilgaauliai batai vasar  komaras, prievarta metro  labai gerai taksistams, riebaus pieno negrimas suminktino mones. Pradkite <a href="https://www.instagram.com/subwaytakes/reel/C9cjPuyu8Bh/">nuo taksi vairuotojo</a>, tskite <a href="https://www.instagram.com/subwaytakes/reel/C40wu4DuEEM/">su pienu</a> ir suinokite <a href="https://www.instagram.com/subwaytakes/reel/C8cZEdgOFft/">koki dviej ri mons tegali igyventi Niujorke</a>. O taip pat skaiiuokite minutes iki kol koks idjikai kdas LT komikas ispjaus ios laidos kopij. <a href="https://www.instagram.com/subwaytakes/">Let them cook! </a></p><div><hr></div><h4><em>Kelions:</em> Lietuva atakuoja Pranczij</h4><p>Praleidau Olimpines Paryiuje, bet gal dar sugausiu lietuvikj kultrin Pranczijos antpuol. Ten verda rimti dalykai. Vienas j: <a href="https://mo.lt/ivykiai/lietuvos-meno-paroda-paryziuje/">MO ir Pompidou partneryst</a>. Keliolika lietuvi meninink jau eksponuojami ir po to bus perleisti (arba jau sigyti) bei nusipelnys vietos nuolatinje Pompidou kolekcijoje. </p><p>Antras j: Krybingumo mokyklos iniciatyva nufilmuotas Linos Lapelyts Baltijos kelio pavertimas iurpiaode muzika. Bsima auditorija taps keli milijonai prancz moksleivi, bet ir ms jauniesiems tai gros nemaiau graiai. Nors su KMo esu susijs esmingai, dalis projekt vyksta be mans ir  stebjau kaip irovas. Ir koks entuziastingas! Bus dar dvi pamokos su Manfredu ir b-girl Nicka. Bet <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UMB-_SiXRDA">pirmiausiai igirskite Linos garsint pavydtin baltijiei drs.</a></p><p>Pasisek pranczams  kiek LT muzikos bus igrota, spektakli, parod ieksponuota, paskait, praneim prasukta, ar Magnetins dainavos silks iragauta. Reikia ten siterpti ir patiems.</p><div><hr></div><h4><em>Tinklalaid:</em> Bandymai suprasti mog #10:  ar manoma be svaiginimosi?</h4><p>Viskas, baigiu savo tinklalaidi brukal. Paskutinysis epizodas apmsto svaigul. Svaigulys  domiai lietuvikai skambanti bsena. Jis yra kakas u normalybs rib. Lyg nesusipratimas aminoje ramybinje normalybje. Svaigulys lietuvikai sako, kad kakas sukasi, nra stabilu, juda, mainosi. Jis tarsi susuka galv, sujaukia prot, sumakaluoja mintis. Juk yra prastyb ir yra svaigulys. Tvarka ir chaosas. Namas ir j supurtantis ems drebjimas.</p><p>Lenkiuosi visiems skyrusiems laiko: Giedriui ir LRT, kurie patikjo alia idja, idealiems panekovams, gars meistravusiam Kristupui, idj kalbjusiai Ulai ir jums, kurie klauste. Laida jau kuris laikas valkatauja ir <a href="https://open.spotify.com/episode/5dYmdd3w934JonWIZCwyND?si=61c1f608a1dd47c5">Spotify</a>, ir <a href="https://www.lrt.lt/mediateka/irasas/2000290180/bandymai-suprasti-zmogu-zmogus-ir-svaiginimasis-ar-imanoma-be-jo">LRT</a>, ir <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1cS6jo8SatY">YouTube</a>.</p><iframe class="spotify-wrap podcast" data-attrs="{&quot;image&quot;:&quot;https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6765630000ba8aa239bea67e217c9690734c6e&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Bandymai suprasti mog. mogus ir svaiginimasis: ar manoma be jo?&quot;,&quot;subtitle&quot;:&quot;LRT&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;Episode&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://open.spotify.com/episode/5dYmdd3w934JonWIZCwyND&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;noScroll&quot;:false}" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/episode/5dYmdd3w934JonWIZCwyND" frameborder="0" gesture="media" allowfullscreen="true" allow="encrypted-media" loading="lazy" data-component-name="Spotify2ToDOM"></iframe><div><hr></div><h4><em>Tyrimas:</em> Geriausias vis laik aktorius</h4><p>Nesiningas, visada kak nuviliantis darbas rinkti geriausius ir dar bandyti objektyviu bti. Daniel Parris nusprend maxsistemikai iskaiiuoti Amerikos aktori-favorit: sudti film vertinimus, pasiekimus kasose ir oskarinius blyksteljimus. Keistoki kriterijai, bet pairime, kas gavosi: #5 Brad Pitt (ha-ha), #4 Jack Nicholson (per emai!), #3 Al Pacino (turi bti tarp geriausi), #2 Paul Newman (gerokai per auktai) ir #1 (labai geras, tik nesutinku, kad geriausias) <a href="https://www.statsignificant.com/p/whos-the-greatest-actor-in-movie">teks paspausti.</a>  </p><div><hr></div><h4><em>Paskaita:</em> Ko galime imokti i 2024-aisiais pasaulyje apdovanot reklam?</h4><p>Jau antrus metus gerai uogauju: keliauju per imtus <em>Cannes Lions</em>, <em>D&amp;AD</em> ir <em>The One Show </em>(trijuose pagrindiniuose rinkodaros ir krybingumo festivaliuose) dekoruot darb ir renku tuos, kurie turi unikalumo jgos bei gali bti gerais pavyzdiais ir kvpjais mums ia, su maesniais biudetais, maiau drsia klientra, ar ribotais resursais. Vilties ybtelti yra, o noro siekti ger rezultat niekas ir neatm. Kvieiu tiek reklamist, tiek klient-rinkodarist iupti savo komandas ir susipainti su keliasdeimt svarbiausi atradim bei pamok. Neprailgs. <a href="https://tickets.paysera.com/lt/event/tomas-ramanauskas-ko-galime-ismokti-is-2024-aisiais-pasaulyje-apdovanotu-reklamu">O bilietai jau juda.</a></p><p>Spalio 10, 10:00 per Zoom. Klaustukai keliauja: <em>bilietai@degadangus.lt</em></p><div><hr></div><h4><em>Deimt dain:</em> The last thing I need is another friend</h4><p>Ajajai koks geras Brokenchord atmosferinis sibavimas, naujas mano DJ set pradios favoritas  El Panda Bear, komunistus aptarianti Molly Nilsson, kosmin 80-j electro ital Patrizia Pellegrino ir pamoka gale nuo J.U.S.: negalvokite apie narkotikus, sako jis. <a href="https://open.spotify.com/playlist/30dJ11nYr2NMhIwxIJcoeR?si=8256dcfd0b4a4273">Grojaratyje</a> rasite ne tik naujausi deimtuk, bet ir visus prie tai buvusius. </p><iframe class="spotify-wrap playlist" data-attrs="{&quot;image&quot;:&quot;https://image-cdn-ak.spotifycdn.com/image/ab67706c0000d72c2df4b1a461e529d1d7a3fbde&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;VARTOTOJO GIDAS&quot;,&quot;subtitle&quot;:&quot;By tmsrmnsks&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;Playlist&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://open.spotify.com/playlist/30dJ11nYr2NMhIwxIJcoeR&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;noScroll&quot;:false}" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/playlist/30dJ11nYr2NMhIwxIJcoeR" frameborder="0" gesture="media" allowfullscreen="true" allow="encrypted-media" loading="lazy" data-component-name="Spotify2ToDOM"></iframe><div><hr></div><h4><em>Laiko vaistymas:</em> urains, banginiai ir poezija</h4><p>Charley Locke sako, jei nori painti mog, <a href="https://www.theatlantic.com/technology/archive/2024/09/notes-app-tours-personal-digital-history/679861/">pairk jo </a><em><a href="https://www.theatlantic.com/technology/archive/2024/09/notes-app-tours-personal-digital-history/679861/">Notes </a></em><a href="https://www.theatlantic.com/technology/archive/2024/09/notes-app-tours-personal-digital-history/679861/">programl</a>: mes joje nesiekiame pasirodyti (nebent esi influenceris 24/7), tad ir suveriame ten tikresnius dalykus, visokius kvailus sraus, minteles, priminimus, btinus pamatymus, ar bsim pasimatym schemas.</p><p>Ei, bangini pamatytojai! <a href="https://happywhale.com/home">Yra svetain</a>, kurioje galite kelti savo regto banginio foto ir GPS koordinates, o mokslininkai su DI pagalba bandys identifikuoti konkret didin. Geriausia pykinti jo uodeg, ji kaip pirt antspaudas  unikali. </p><p>Mokytis poezij mintinai yra sveikas usimimas, t girdjome jau. Bet mokytis gerai ne tik dl atminties struktr tvirtinimo, o pirmiausiai dl jos <a href="https://archive.is/HWHFk#selection-519.3-519.42">audimo  savo mstym</a>, kuris po siminto krinio turtja ir auga.</p><div><hr></div><h4><em>Citata:</em> apie laim, k daugiau </h4><p><strong>Mes niekada negyvename, mes tikims gyventi, ir, nuolatos ruodamiesi laimei, neivengiamai niekada nebsime laimingi.</strong></p><p><em>Blaise Pascal (nujojau i Literatros ir meno pagirtojo numerio.</em></p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://tickets.paysera.com/lt/event/tomas-ramanauskas-ko-galime-ismokti-is-2024-aisiais-pasaulyje-apdovanotu-reklamu" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8bdf8a59-9ccf-433c-92dc-f3cc108f22fd_1528x1350.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8bdf8a59-9ccf-433c-92dc-f3cc108f22fd_1528x1350.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8bdf8a59-9ccf-433c-92dc-f3cc108f22fd_1528x1350.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8bdf8a59-9ccf-433c-92dc-f3cc108f22fd_1528x1350.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8bdf8a59-9ccf-433c-92dc-f3cc108f22fd_1528x1350.png" width="1456" height="1286" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/8bdf8a59-9ccf-433c-92dc-f3cc108f22fd_1528x1350.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1286,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:2678694,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;https://tickets.paysera.com/lt/event/tomas-ramanauskas-ko-galime-ismokti-is-2024-aisiais-pasaulyje-apdovanotu-reklamu&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8bdf8a59-9ccf-433c-92dc-f3cc108f22fd_1528x1350.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8bdf8a59-9ccf-433c-92dc-f3cc108f22fd_1528x1350.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8bdf8a59-9ccf-433c-92dc-f3cc108f22fd_1528x1350.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8bdf8a59-9ccf-433c-92dc-f3cc108f22fd_1528x1350.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div></div></div></a></figure></div></body></html>	Kultros leidini kokyb vidutinika, bet "Literatra ir menas" + "Le Monde" numeris isiskiria. Rekomenduojama sigyti. Knygose - mokslo ir gyvn temos. Filmuose - prancz klasika. Lietuvos menas keliauja  Pranczij. Nauja tinklalaid apie svaigul. Tyrimas irinko geriausi aktori. Paskaita apie apdovanotas reklamas. Naujos dainos ir doms laiko vaistymo bdai.	2024-09-17 04:46:00	2024-10-08 12:03:05.377	2024-10-08 15:33:44.032	{lithuanian}	https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9268610f-60be-4329-be44-6e9a53e03144_2160x1346.png	Tomas Ramanauskas	vartotojo-gidas-rugsjui
84	https://emilijaviso.substack.com/p/puff-daddy-9-ryskiausi-rugsejo-albumai	Puff Daddy + 9 rykiausi rugsjo albumai (23)	Kriminalins naujienos	<html><head></head><body><blockquote><h4>Kriminalins naujienos</h4></blockquote><p>Kol Lietuvoj laukiam daugiau pletk apie tai, ko Dailius Dargis imoko raydamas knygas apie mafijozus, visgi svarbiausia pastarojo mnesio, o turbt ir vis i bei ateinani met muzikos pasaulio naujiena  Seanas Combsas, kitaip inomas kaip Puff Daddy, P. Diddy, Diddy ir Brother Love, yra sulaikytas, jam pareikta visa krva kaltinim  dl reketo, seksualinio inaudojimo, smurto, sutenerysts, priverstinio darbo, papirkinjimo ir t. t. Jo verslo imperija kaltinimo tekste prilyginta mafijos sindikatui, kurio nariai (darbuotojai) dangst nusikaltimus, trukd teisingumui, grasino ir pan.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8f7668c2-bd2d-47ee-8fbd-c2f235c85443_957x540.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8f7668c2-bd2d-47ee-8fbd-c2f235c85443_957x540.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8f7668c2-bd2d-47ee-8fbd-c2f235c85443_957x540.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8f7668c2-bd2d-47ee-8fbd-c2f235c85443_957x540.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8f7668c2-bd2d-47ee-8fbd-c2f235c85443_957x540.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8f7668c2-bd2d-47ee-8fbd-c2f235c85443_957x540.png" width="506" height="285.51724137931035" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/8f7668c2-bd2d-47ee-8fbd-c2f235c85443_957x540.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:540,&quot;width&quot;:957,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:506,&quot;bytes&quot;:1070980,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8f7668c2-bd2d-47ee-8fbd-c2f235c85443_957x540.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8f7668c2-bd2d-47ee-8fbd-c2f235c85443_957x540.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8f7668c2-bd2d-47ee-8fbd-c2f235c85443_957x540.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8f7668c2-bd2d-47ee-8fbd-c2f235c85443_957x540.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><p>Advokatas Buzbie (akivaizdiai nusiteiks prie rep, nes 2021 m. ikl 750 mln. doleri iekin kitai repo vaigdei Travis Scottui, kurio festivalyje Astroworld mirtinai suspausta 10 moni) paskelb atstovaujantis 120 asmen  60 moter, 60 vyr; 25 i j nusikalstamos veikos metu (pradedant 1991 m.) buvo nepilnameiai (vienas buvo 9-eri).</p><p>Viskas prasidjo, kai prie metus Diddy ex-mergina Casandra Ventura padav j  teism, kaltindama ilgamete prievarta bei seksualiniu inaudojimu, taip pat siekiu kontroliuoti kiekvien jos gyvenimo aspekt. Tada pasirod viebuio stebjimo kamer ufiksuotas sukreiantis <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3Ti0hUQPy5U&amp;t=7s&amp;ab_channel=CNN">video</a>, kuriame bgani Cassie atsiveja rankluosiu apsiris Diddy ir primua. Nors su mergina pavyko finansikai (ar kaip kitaip) susitarti, pasirod kit moter kaltinimai dl svaiginimo narkotikais, seksualins prievartos, smurto filmavimo ir rodymo draugams</p><p>Dar kovo mn.  Combso vilas Los Andele ir Majamyje spdingai siver brys FTB agent. Skelbiama, kad konfiskuota krva ginkl ir amunicijos, taip pat labai per didel kolekcija aliej kdikiams ir lubrikant. Combsas dabar neileidiamas u ustat ir nuolat stebimas (galimai dl saviudybs rizikos). </p><div id="youtube2-aC4BC-Hxq9g" class="youtube-wrap" data-attrs="{&quot;videoId&quot;:&quot;aC4BC-Hxq9g&quot;,&quot;startTime&quot;:null,&quot;endTime&quot;:null}" data-component-name="Youtube2ToDOM"><div class="youtube-inner"><iframe src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/aC4BC-Hxq9g?rel=0&amp;autoplay=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;enablejsapi=0" frameborder="0" loading="lazy" gesture="media" allow="autoplay; fullscreen" allowautoplay="true" allowfullscreen="true" width="728" height="409"></iframe></div></div><p>Man asmenikai Puff Daddy visad pirmiausia buvo Jennifer Lopez bias ir dar ito spdingo mashupo su Led Zeppelin Kashmir autorius. Bet jei galvojat, kad jis seniai pamirtas ir nebesvarbus, tai inokit, kad 2022 m. jo turtas vertintas milijardu doleri, jis yra antras turtingiausias reperis po Jay Z (babkes jam krauna vodkos, drabui, kvepal, televizijos, aidim investicijos). Dabar gi i jo atimtas garbs laipsnis Howardo universitete ir simbolinis Niujorko raktas.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5cb9a795-bbc0-4921-850a-4e6f87363633_813x572.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5cb9a795-bbc0-4921-850a-4e6f87363633_813x572.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5cb9a795-bbc0-4921-850a-4e6f87363633_813x572.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5cb9a795-bbc0-4921-850a-4e6f87363633_813x572.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5cb9a795-bbc0-4921-850a-4e6f87363633_813x572.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5cb9a795-bbc0-4921-850a-4e6f87363633_813x572.png" width="464" height="326.4551045510455" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/5cb9a795-bbc0-4921-850a-4e6f87363633_813x572.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:572,&quot;width&quot;:813,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:464,&quot;bytes&quot;:775489,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5cb9a795-bbc0-4921-850a-4e6f87363633_813x572.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5cb9a795-bbc0-4921-850a-4e6f87363633_813x572.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5cb9a795-bbc0-4921-850a-4e6f87363633_813x572.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5cb9a795-bbc0-4921-850a-4e6f87363633_813x572.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><p>Aiku, iuo metu dreba tikrai ne vienas ou verslo atstovas, nes adama atskleisti daugiau dideli vard, mielai dalyvavusi pagarsjusiuose Diddy vakarliuose  Freak Offs. Pasak advokato, itie pariai ir afterpariai vykdavo albumo ileidimo, Naujako, Liepos 4osios proga, taip pat puppy parties, all white parties... Ten vykdavo sekso ou tarp sekso darbuotoj ir, galimai, apsvaigint dalyvi. Vakarli srauose yra Ashton Kutcher, Jennifer Lopez, Will Smith, Sarah Jessica Parker, Leonardo DiCaprio, Beyonc, Khloe Kardashian.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff061ea6a-9479-4da6-b210-77e9cab1655d_703x707.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff061ea6a-9479-4da6-b210-77e9cab1655d_703x707.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff061ea6a-9479-4da6-b210-77e9cab1655d_703x707.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff061ea6a-9479-4da6-b210-77e9cab1655d_703x707.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff061ea6a-9479-4da6-b210-77e9cab1655d_703x707.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff061ea6a-9479-4da6-b210-77e9cab1655d_703x707.png" width="369" height="371.09957325746797" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/f061ea6a-9479-4da6-b210-77e9cab1655d_703x707.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:707,&quot;width&quot;:703,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:369,&quot;bytes&quot;:923191,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff061ea6a-9479-4da6-b210-77e9cab1655d_703x707.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff061ea6a-9479-4da6-b210-77e9cab1655d_703x707.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff061ea6a-9479-4da6-b210-77e9cab1655d_703x707.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff061ea6a-9479-4da6-b210-77e9cab1655d_703x707.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">Ten gale Leo, teigiantis, kad su Diddy nuo t laik nebebendravo </figcaption></figure></div><p>Combsas taip pat yra nuo seno pagarsjs jaun talent globjas. Jo prote Usheris pasakoja paauglystje beveik metus gyvens su Diddy/Daddy, kur mat dalyk ir buvo supaindintas su sekso vairove. Taip pat su Diddy laik leido mautis Bieberis, kuriam itas dd <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kxHwfTpQjpc&amp;ab_channel=JustinBieber">dovanojo main</a> ir adjo nam. Tiesa, per tiktokus dabar persiritusi neva niekur neskelbta Bieberio daina su odiais <em>Lost myself at a Diddy party, didnt know thats how it go, I was in it for a new Ferrari, but it cost me way more than my soul, wasnt worth all the fortune and fame</em> vis dlto tikriausiai yra sukurta dirbtinio intelekto.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F686d8a68-bbf6-4788-bd43-a780ade09921_1057x531.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F686d8a68-bbf6-4788-bd43-a780ade09921_1057x531.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F686d8a68-bbf6-4788-bd43-a780ade09921_1057x531.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F686d8a68-bbf6-4788-bd43-a780ade09921_1057x531.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F686d8a68-bbf6-4788-bd43-a780ade09921_1057x531.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F686d8a68-bbf6-4788-bd43-a780ade09921_1057x531.png" width="578" height="290.3670766319773" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/686d8a68-bbf6-4788-bd43-a780ade09921_1057x531.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:531,&quot;width&quot;:1057,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:578,&quot;bytes&quot;:820404,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F686d8a68-bbf6-4788-bd43-a780ade09921_1057x531.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F686d8a68-bbf6-4788-bd43-a780ade09921_1057x531.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F686d8a68-bbf6-4788-bd43-a780ade09921_1057x531.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F686d8a68-bbf6-4788-bd43-a780ade09921_1057x531.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption"></figcaption></figure></div><p>Diddy vakarliais ne vienas yra ir vieai lyktjsis. 50 Cent, pavyzdiui, nuo seno nekenia Pafio ir sak, kad n u k neit  jo tsus, nes Diddy mgsta apkabinti i priekio ir galo vienu metu. Taip pat Diddy galimai yra kviets 50 Cent pasiopinti. Ir 50, ir Eminemas ne kart yra repav ir apie sen legend/ties, kad Diddy usak Tupaco nuudym. </p><p>Tiesa, laukiam ir kriminalini P. Diddy ssaj su R. Kelly (ne veltui gi tokie vardai), kuris, 2019 m. pasirodius spdingai tiriamajai dokumentikai Surviving R. Kelly (rekomenduoju), buvo nuteistas 30 met kaljimo u reket, seksualin smurt, vaik pornografij ir ilgamet nepilnamei inaudojim.</p><div><hr></div><blockquote><h4>Nauji albumai</h4></blockquote><p><em>Nesu apsisprendus, kaip reitinguoti albumus ar bent kaip juos irikiuoti (galit pasilyt), nes blogi albumai man irgi doms ir kartais sukelia daugiau mini nei geri. Tai tiesiog, kad jus panervuoiau, raau Jovan pirmu numeriu, o paskui pereisiu prie diazo. Pabaigai palikau geriausi.</em></p><div class="image-gallery-embed" data-attrs="{&quot;gallery&quot;:{&quot;images&quot;:[{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/2cf7acba-50a5-4b39-b1da-2509e691187b_711x730.png&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/e3611ef2-7435-48ae-ab61-5470c575c55c_2091x1877.jpeg&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/1242712c-9b1c-471b-a299-d3688ae08e82_718x717.png&quot;}],&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;staticGalleryImage&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/2def481a-a183-4441-b948-3e772a60c270_1456x474.png&quot;}},&quot;isEditorNode&quot;:true}"></div><p><strong>(I) JOVANI Noriu okt</strong></p><iframe class="spotify-wrap album" data-attrs="{&quot;image&quot;:&quot;https://i.scdn.co/image/ab67616d0000b2730a98d9f1256c9ad453b2ec81&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Noriu okt&quot;,&quot;subtitle&quot;:&quot;Jovani, Ledi Ais&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;Album&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://open.spotify.com/album/6PiqXDe7wIJjhsiObo4LXx&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;noScroll&quot;:false}" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/album/6PiqXDe7wIJjhsiObo4LXx" frameborder="0" gesture="media" allowfullscreen="true" allow="encrypted-media" loading="lazy" data-component-name="Spotify2ToDOM"></iframe><p>Mano feisbuko burbule Diovanis, drauge su Bareikiu ir Prsaiiu, turbt yra tie trys nekeniamiausi muzikos pasaulio tigrai. Tiek vargas Diovanis keiksnojamas, kad man jau net norisi protestuot, prieintis inercijai ir sakyt, kad nugi nieko jis blogo nedaro. Tokias mintis sustiprino <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UV9c7YZJeeI&amp;t=4371s&amp;ab_channel=Lietuvosnacionalinisradijasirtelevizija">Zilnio pokalbis su Nainiu</a>, kur is savo firminiu itin ramiu ir mandagiu tonu gana blaiviai vertina savo kryb ir kit poir  j. spdingiausia, kai savo kryb palygina su greito maisto restoranu. Taip pat keliskart kartoja, kad savo temoj, tiems monms, kuriems a groju, a tikrai moku padaryt ger laik, daug darbo dedu, kad mons gaut vent.</p><p>Kiek tragikomikiau skamba pasakojimas apie Jovanio apsilankym Opiume, kai kakas j pasiunt nx (nors man gi gali visokia muzika patikt), ir jo atsakas kritikams: Kaip a galiu nemokt grot, jei t esu dars jau tkstanius valand. Na, ia ikyla terminologinis klausimas  k vadinsime grojimu. Ar melodijos atitaikym prie vizulki ekrane galime vadinti grojimu? Slidi ta riba, tarp elektronins muzikos krybos, sen pamirt krini remiksavimo, priklimo naujam gyvenimui, ir  naudojimosi kit kryba savo materialinio pralobimo tikslais.</p><p>Ta riba slidinja ir Jovani savo albume, kuris man turbt labiausiai nepatinka tuo, kad Jovani vardas raomas pirmiau originalaus krinio atlikj. Juk jeigu bt urayta Jurga Nebijok (Jovani remix), viskas bt kaip ir aiku ir nedomu. </p><p>Tokio albumo, kuriame patiuninguotos senos (pagyvenusios) lietuvikos dainos, motyvacij Jovanis aikina tuo, kad lietuvika muzika atgim, vl tapo domi, seni gabalai buvo rayti labai prasta kokybe, norisi, kad jie skambt iuolaikikai. ia vl terminologinis klausimas - kas tas iuolaikikai? Bet suprantu, kad didelei daliai moni patinka mainoj sijungt ger ritmuk. Be to, kaip pasakoja Nainys, visiems iems autoriams buvo paskambinta, visi jie sutiko bendradarbiauti ir galimai netgi pasirodys Jovani Arena Show. Tikrai galiu sutikt dl prastos Junior ar Ledi Ais ra kokybs. Tos dainos tikrai nusipelno ir antro, ir treio gyvenimo. Bet ar tas pats galioja Jurgai ir Lemon Joy? Taip pat kakaip nemalonu matyti, kad itie Jovanio remiksai dabar perklausomis prilygsta arba lenkia originalus.</p><p>Taip pat nuvilia, kad albume net trys Junior gabalai  turbt su jais geriausiai pavyko suvaibint. Bet jei jau daroma tokia lietuviko pop kompiliacija, nortsi jos vairesns. Kur Ekspreso Pirmoji naktis? Kur Dinamika? </p><p>Prasmingiausiai, inoma, skamba du gabalai su Remio Retro repu, nes nuo remikso priartja prie koverio. Dar patiko Tajos Jra (gal todl, kad neatsimenu originalo). </p><p>Ai, dar interviu patiko Jovanio <em>rantas </em>apie tai, kad uuot piktinsi ir bjauriai apie j komentav, geriau paraykit inut, galsi manim pasinaudot, a tau duosiu vis savo auditorij, galsim sukolabint. Kaip pats pripaino, gal ir naivus poiris, bet visgi graus. Jei komercinis poiris jums nesvetimas.</p><div><hr></div><p><strong>(II) NOTE LITHUANIA: Jazz 2024</strong></p><iframe class="spotify-wrap playlist" data-attrs="{&quot;image&quot;:&quot;https://image-cdn-ak.spotifycdn.com/image/ab67706c0000d72cfff8f60888060ec58ac7d69d&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Note Lithuania: Jazz 2024&quot;,&quot;subtitle&quot;:&quot;By Greta Jakobsonait&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;Playlist&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://open.spotify.com/playlist/0f1cDsBQs6tApRCaFgTFZg&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;noScroll&quot;:false}" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/playlist/0f1cDsBQs6tApRCaFgTFZg" frameborder="0" gesture="media" allowfullscreen="true" allow="encrypted-media" loading="lazy" data-component-name="Spotify2ToDOM"></iframe><p>Spalio 1620 d. vyks turbt labiausiai gerbiamas ir, mano akimis, labiausiai saugotinas Lietuvos festivalis  <a href="http://www.vilniusjazz.lt/">Vilnius Jazz</a>. Ne vienus metus esu ten save edukavus, nes programoje visada galima rasti ir aus nelauanio klasikinio diazo, ir beprotiko avangardo, ir Lietuvos diazo istorijos, ir naujok, ir tolim, ir artim krat. Tai ten silau eiti.</p><p>O taipogi silau susipainti su Lietuvos muzikos informacijos centro atrinktais pastarj poros met domiausiais diazo kriniais. Rinktin sumanyta skatinti muzikos sklaidai usienyje, bet tikrai turt bti labiau pasitelkiama ir sklaidai Lietuvoje. Rinktin vairiaanr, vairiastil ir vairiainstrument, nuo mylim Sheep Got Waxed iki dideli tarptautini ansambli.</p><p>Apskritai Note Lithuania rinkiniai man atrodo nekainojamos verts. (Dal j galite rasti <a href="https://www.mic.lt/lt/grotuvas/">MIC grotuve</a>. O vis krv seniausi, nuo 2007 m., <a href="https://www.pakartot.lt/project/note-lithuania">rasite Pakartot</a>. Labai nortsi, kad jie visi tapt patogiai prieinami vienoj vietoj.) Juose galima matyti lietuvikos muzikos, atskir jos anr, kait bgant metams. Prisiminti, pavyzdiui, kaip 2007 m. muzikos bta tiek maai, kad rinkinyje buvo apjungtos pop/rock kategorijos, ir kaip net Riaubikyt (buvo ir ji) dainavo anglikai.</p><p>Tiesa, dar patikslinsiu, kad dabar kriniai komisijos atrenkami i atsist paraik, t. y. ia nebtinai rasite kok nors akivaizd atlikj, nes jis tiesiog nedalyvavo konkurse. Taiau galit rasti kok nors visai neinom, kuris nepatingjo dalyvauti. <a href="https://emilijaviso.substack.com/p/menesio-suktinis">ia pernai raiau</a> apie Note Lithuania eksperimentikos rinkin.</p><div><hr></div><p><strong>(III) JAZZU Keisti enklai</strong></p><iframe class="spotify-wrap album" data-attrs="{&quot;image&quot;:&quot;https://i.scdn.co/image/ab67616d0000b2734e709a992173730d57a8c82e&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Keisti enklai&quot;,&quot;subtitle&quot;:&quot;Jazzu&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;Album&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://open.spotify.com/album/1QcYd3zOjvXO3ZYGJ71Umw&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;noScroll&quot;:false}" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/album/1QcYd3zOjvXO3ZYGJ71Umw" frameborder="0" gesture="media" allowfullscreen="true" allow="encrypted-media" loading="lazy" data-component-name="Spotify2ToDOM"></iframe><p>Labai man grai dramatika daina Igriau irkiau, kur nerpestingu tonu pasakojama apie galimai toksikus buvusius santykius. Pana naratyv kitais odiais pasakoja ir Vilkolakis. Albumai gal nra stipriausia Jazzu pus. Ir is nra vientisas (nepadeda ir pridti intro bei outro), labiau paremtas atskirais hitais (puikiu lengvabdiku duetu su Gamka). iek tiek cringeo sukl krinys Garsiai ploju sau, kuriame i ties yra sau plojama. Vis dlto i Jazzu neatimsi ilavintos poptekst raymo rankos.</p><p>inau, kad daug k atstumia Jazzu manieros, bet manau, kad labai svarbu vertinti jos talent bei ilgamet stabili karjer. Nedaug teturim tokio rykumo bei takingumo moter, o toki div su jos pliusais ir minusais apskritai teturim vien. Dukart teko bti Jazzu ir Somovo areniniuose koncertuose, kurie simin spdingu Justs, kaip atlikjos, talentu, ne tik vokaliniu, bet ir emociniu. Daug kas sako: vis ird atiduodu, bet ten tikrai tai jautsi.</p><div><hr></div><div class="image-gallery-embed" data-attrs="{&quot;gallery&quot;:{&quot;images&quot;:[{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/78c33039-221c-440c-944e-f3e3a09eb68b_716x720.png&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/5fe56d9c-143c-4f6f-bbce-cb18b39077e0_1200x1200.jpeg&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/392d762c-9085-4fa4-a3fc-a3e599924192_715x721.png&quot;}],&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;staticGalleryImage&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/5fb35cdd-630e-4046-996a-40eba2fded0c_1456x474.png&quot;}},&quot;isEditorNode&quot;:true}"></div><p><strong>(IV) MCLOUD God Is Overrated</strong></p><iframe class="spotify-wrap album" data-attrs="{&quot;image&quot;:&quot;https://i.scdn.co/image/ab67616d0000b273b5f4712f4bf473fe33c23864&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;GOD IS OVERRATED&quot;,&quot;subtitle&quot;:&quot;McLoud&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;Album&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://open.spotify.com/album/3PwjNf7UsXOKZoV3i2FaeA&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;noScroll&quot;:false}" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/album/3PwjNf7UsXOKZoV3i2FaeA" frameborder="0" gesture="media" allowfullscreen="true" allow="encrypted-media" loading="lazy" data-component-name="Spotify2ToDOM"></iframe><p>Jau 5tas McLoud albumas. Kaip bga laikas. Pavadinimas Dievas pervertintas grina prie pirmojo - Dievo nuleisti. Ir pasakoja, kaip Kristus randamas kakokiam afteryje Rusijoje. Kaip patys sak LRT Opus, anksiau kastruodavom graulius, dabar kastruojam ventuosius. Tai tokie reikaliukai. McLoudai tsia savo provokacijas, kurios visgi lieka pasiaidimo, pasilinksminimo lygmeny ar bent taip yra priimamos jaunos publikos. Jei bt kiti laikai, gal visi drauge sudegint kokio politiko main. Dabar gi grup sako: Lietuva eina  priek, nes mes i vasar gyvenam i miesto veni. itas paradoksalus faktas mane ir diugina (dl to, kad regionai sulaukia iek tiek daugiau iek tiek vairesns muzikos nei anksiau), ir kartu kakaip lidina.</p><div><hr></div><p><strong>(V) NOYUS Salva Xalva</strong></p><div class="bandcamp-wrap album" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://noyus.bandcamp.com/album/salva-xalva&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Salva Xalva, by Noyus&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;9 track album&quot;,&quot;thumbnail_url&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/5e2f4547-5b8e-411a-af10-451299627cf4_700x700.jpeg&quot;,&quot;author&quot;:&quot;Noyus&quot;,&quot;embed_url&quot;:&quot;https://bandcamp.com/EmbeddedPlayer/album=1718871262/size=large/bgcol=ffffff/linkcol=333333/artwork=small/transparent=true/&quot;,&quot;is_album&quot;:true}" data-component-name="BandcampToDOM"><iframe src="https://bandcamp.com/EmbeddedPlayer/album=1718871262/size=large/bgcol=ffffff/linkcol=333333/artwork=small/transparent=true/" frameborder="0" gesture="media" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen="true"></iframe></div><p>Jei iekote velnaus skambesio, lidno okio, queer pop ar tiesiog kvpimo savarankikai kurti, Noyus ra labai asmenik, trap album apie vienatv, meils iekojim ir bijojim, geism ir atsiribojim. Singlas In Your Room man yra viena graiausi i met dain.</p><div id="youtube2-9QKm83BbyoI" class="youtube-wrap" data-attrs="{&quot;videoId&quot;:&quot;9QKm83BbyoI&quot;,&quot;startTime&quot;:null,&quot;endTime&quot;:null}" data-component-name="Youtube2ToDOM"><div class="youtube-inner"><iframe src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/9QKm83BbyoI?rel=0&amp;autoplay=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;enablejsapi=0" frameborder="0" loading="lazy" gesture="media" allow="autoplay; fullscreen" allowautoplay="true" allowfullscreen="true" width="728" height="409"></iframe></div></div><div><hr></div><p><strong>(VI) DESPOTIN FAM Geros naujienos</strong></p><iframe class="spotify-wrap album" data-attrs="{&quot;image&quot;:&quot;https://i.scdn.co/image/ab67616d0000b273a636b3722441e27cd0702cdd&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;GEROS NAUJIENOS&quot;,&quot;subtitle&quot;:&quot;Despotin Fam, DJ Swix&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;Album&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://open.spotify.com/album/65AxQyGn2IkZezXhD42EaC&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;noScroll&quot;:false}" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/album/65AxQyGn2IkZezXhD42EaC" frameborder="0" gesture="media" allowfullscreen="true" allow="encrypted-media" loading="lazy" data-component-name="Spotify2ToDOM"></iframe><p>I bibliotekos dabar esu pasimus Roberto Bolao knyg 2666  jos apimtis vir 850 puslapi, tai itas 58 minui trukms albumas iek tiek j primin. Jei rayiau rimt recenzij, reikt tam paskirt bent jau atskir dien. Tai gerai, kad muzika galima mgautis ir pernelyg nesigilinant, galima atsiduoti jos bangoms, itiems 13 krini, kabintis u paskir eilui (patiko ita rimavimo kelion: <em>nardymo <strong>kur</strong>sai - ap<strong>kurs</strong>ti nuo gylio - pratsimas <strong>bus</strong> dar - i tuio nepri<strong>bur</strong>si - neprau<strong>st</strong>a <strong>bur</strong>na kaip im<strong>puls</strong>as - eks<strong>kurs</strong>ija - e<strong>muls</strong>ija - kon<strong>vuls</strong>ij - kada pri<strong>guls</strong>iu</em>), u ndnesni/suauglikesni ir smagesni/paikesni melodij (smagiausiai suskambjo Visk aikint). </p><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://emilijaviso.substack.com/subscribe?&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Subscribe now&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"><a class="button primary" href="https://emilijaviso.substack.com/subscribe?"><span>Subscribe now</span></a></p><p>Despotin Fam ivengia to repo scen nuodijanio naivaus susireikminimo, ilieka kiek nuoaly, pernelyg nesiplaiksto, kartu isaugodami ir stiprindami savo kult, su laiku gerdami, prie scenos jau stovint draug vaikams. Ai, ir jie ov vien geriausi i met klip.</p><div id="youtube2-4HMXRtR3Og4" class="youtube-wrap" data-attrs="{&quot;videoId&quot;:&quot;4HMXRtR3Og4&quot;,&quot;startTime&quot;:null,&quot;endTime&quot;:null}" data-component-name="Youtube2ToDOM"><div class="youtube-inner"><iframe src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/4HMXRtR3Og4?rel=0&amp;autoplay=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;enablejsapi=0" frameborder="0" loading="lazy" gesture="media" allow="autoplay; fullscreen" allowautoplay="true" allowfullscreen="true" width="728" height="409"></iframe></div></div><div><hr></div><div class="image-gallery-embed" data-attrs="{&quot;gallery&quot;:{&quot;images&quot;:[{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/5aa57216-9d82-4997-bbe5-ad6709ba36d8_1200x1200.jpeg&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/dcac3ec8-7ccf-4a74-b725-ee4d8145ea73_708x697.png&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/ef081fd9-ec55-49c6-b417-8291a60fbe00_717x712.png&quot;}],&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;staticGalleryImage&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/e3305d07-b140-4029-881e-919765644cd6_1456x474.png&quot;}},&quot;isEditorNode&quot;:true}"></div><p><strong>(VII) PLI We Know Exactly What Were Doing</strong></p><div class="bandcamp-wrap album" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://plie.bandcamp.com/album/we-know-exactly-what-were-doing&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;We Know Exactly What We're Doing, by Pli&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;13 track album&quot;,&quot;thumbnail_url&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/7ea660d7-8bad-40e9-aafb-840b13d75a62_700x700.jpeg&quot;,&quot;author&quot;:&quot;Pli&quot;,&quot;embed_url&quot;:&quot;https://bandcamp.com/EmbeddedPlayer/album=2557294927/size=large/bgcol=ffffff/linkcol=333333/artwork=small/transparent=true/&quot;,&quot;is_album&quot;:true}" data-component-name="BandcampToDOM"><iframe src="https://bandcamp.com/EmbeddedPlayer/album=2557294927/size=large/bgcol=ffffff/linkcol=333333/artwork=small/transparent=true/" frameborder="0" gesture="media" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen="true"></iframe></div><p>Jei neturit kur dt emocini jg, galit jas sudti  io ekstremalaus albumo klausym. Tai antras Pli darbas, mano supratimu, per ilgas (43 min.), bet tikrai spdingas ir gyvastingas, t. y. gyvai skambantis, nenuglostytas. Lietuvos muzikos emlapyje grup nariais dalinasi su Motina, Keista bjauria uvim, Tureto sindromu  tai vien i i grupi skirtingumo galima susidaryt spd apie Pli chaotikum, teatralikum ir Death Gripsikum. </p><p>Patinka ironikas albumo pavadinimas ir apskritai pats faktas, kad kakas skiria laik ir energij btent tokiai krybai, praskiedianiai, prapjaunaniai tai, kas lengva, malonu, standartika.</p><p>Rekomenduoju D. Kunino interviu su vokalistu <a href="https://www.mic.lt/lt/ivykiai/2024/09/28/triuksmingi-plie-eksperimentai-zagina-roko-mitologija/?fbclid=IwY2xjawFsosBleHRuA2FlbQIxMAABHT_T5jvOIKrmj7BBD9XX4yOUSLc-9k566eivChhInLVrzEVJ7xilnz1BLg_aem_K4iddiFktg6Wc_xOlhWSzg">MIC svetainje</a>. Ten suinosite, kad is albumas  tai naujasis karaliaus arlzo III portretas. Beklausydami muzikos galit apsilankyti ir <a href="https://plievoid.com/">ezoteriniame grups puslapyje</a>. O geriausia tai bt apsilankyti koncerte, nes Pli nemaai turuoja po Europ ir scenoj smogia i peties. </p><div id="youtube2-c1cYeIXgk2U" class="youtube-wrap" data-attrs="{&quot;videoId&quot;:&quot;c1cYeIXgk2U&quot;,&quot;startTime&quot;:null,&quot;endTime&quot;:null}" data-component-name="Youtube2ToDOM"><div class="youtube-inner"><iframe src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/c1cYeIXgk2U?rel=0&amp;autoplay=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;enablejsapi=0" frameborder="0" loading="lazy" gesture="media" allow="autoplay; fullscreen" allowautoplay="true" allowfullscreen="true" width="728" height="409"></iframe></div></div><div><hr></div><p><strong>(VIII) BROKENCHORD Stone Island Tracks</strong></p><div class="bandcamp-wrap album" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://brokenchord.bandcamp.com/album/stone-island-tracks&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Stone Island Tracks, by Brokenchord&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;7 track album&quot;,&quot;thumbnail_url&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/4d9c3ec4-6e2b-4155-bf2e-73adfa65025e_700x700.jpeg&quot;,&quot;author&quot;:&quot;Brokenchord&quot;,&quot;embed_url&quot;:&quot;https://bandcamp.com/EmbeddedPlayer/album=814773176/size=large/bgcol=ffffff/linkcol=333333/artwork=small/transparent=true/&quot;,&quot;is_album&quot;:true}" data-component-name="BandcampToDOM"><iframe src="https://bandcamp.com/EmbeddedPlayer/album=814773176/size=large/bgcol=ffffff/linkcol=333333/artwork=small/transparent=true/" frameborder="0" gesture="media" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen="true"></iframe></div><p>2011 m. solinis projektas Brokenchord susilauk dmesio i Radiohead, remiksavo j krin, vliau Ernesto miksas skambjo BBC Radio One eksperimentikos laidoje. Jei Lietuvoj egzistuot muzikos urnalistika ir visi portalai skelbt geriausi met album topus, 2017 m. Endless Transmission ten, idealiame pasaulyje, tikrai bt.</p><p>Naujasis albumas taip pat vykis, tegu ir ne visi t ino. Autorius j dedikuoja kelionms automobiliu, tad visi mainistai galit ibandyti. Mane itas gitaros ir elektronikos lo-fi opusas stebina kuoptumu, subtilumu ir beodiu ikalbingumu.</p><div><hr></div><h4><em>Rykiausias mnesio albumas</em></h4><p><strong>(IX) AKEDYA Akedya</strong></p><iframe class="spotify-wrap album" data-attrs="{&quot;image&quot;:&quot;https://i.scdn.co/image/ab67616d0000b273e54c9e6ad7770314b6b41eb3&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Akedya&quot;,&quot;subtitle&quot;:&quot;Akedya&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;Album&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://open.spotify.com/album/2aYby13hgEbf7Ta9EH7M2L&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;noScroll&quot;:false}" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/album/2aYby13hgEbf7Ta9EH7M2L" frameborder="0" gesture="media" allowfullscreen="true" allow="encrypted-media" loading="lazy" data-component-name="Spotify2ToDOM"></iframe><p>Didiausias mnesio atradimas ir labiausiai  save trauks albumas. Akedya  kvintetas, susijungs i labai skirting lauk: akademins muzikos, metalo (Juodvarnis), diazo, eksperimentikos (Motina). ia ir postrokas, ir tmingos Nick Caveikos raudos, ir smuiko dejons, ir savotika intensyvi, energinga apatija (lot. <em>acedia </em> apatija, abejingumas). Originalus tirtos tamsos garso takelis, kur sivaizduoju skambant teatro scenoje.</p><div><hr></div><p>Kai raau itas nauj album apvalgas, tikrai jauiuosi, tarsi darb dirbiau. Nes pastangos ir laikas neproporcingi moraliniam atpildui. Visgi atrodo svarbu pabaksnoti pirtu  kuo vairesnius albumus, juolab kad maai kas t daro. Jei muzikos jums dar nepakanka, labai rekomenduoju pasinerti  milinik <a href="https://www.mic.lt/lt/ivykiai/2024/09/30/2024-uju-i-ojo-pusmecio-lietuvisku-albumu-apzvalga/">Vitalijaus Gailiaus album apvalg MICe</a>. Medal jam u tekstus.</p><p>O man galite atsilyginti irdele, komentaru, pasidalinimu soc.medijose arba  pinigais! Paspaud mygtuk emiau, galsite vesti savo norim sum.</p><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://buy.stripe.com/4gw7tv5Tj63OfGUdQR&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Duoti pinig&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"><a class="button primary" href="https://buy.stripe.com/4gw7tv5Tj63OfGUdQR"><span>Duoti pinig</span></a></p><div class="pullquote"><p><em><strong>it ir dar daugiau dmesio vertos muzikos visad rasite mano nuolat pildomame Spotify grojaratyje <a href="https://open.spotify.com/playlist/44kNZfhwgSLhg5iLNczrH0?si=bff2c7551b2345d8">New Lithuanian Music</a>.</strong></em></p></div></body></html>	Seanas Combsas (Puff Daddy) sulaikytas, kaltinamas daugybe nusikaltim. Jo verslo imperija prilyginta mafijos sindikatui. Advokatas atstovauja 120 asmen, skaitant nepilnameius. FTB siver  Combso namus, konfiskavo ginklus. Combsas neileidiamas u ustat. Kiti yms asmenys gali bti traukti  skandal.	2024-10-04 13:18:28	2024-10-08 12:03:11.215	2024-10-08 15:33:44.247	{lithuanian}	https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8f7668c2-bd2d-47ee-8fbd-c2f235c85443_957x540.png	Emilija Visockait	puff-daddy-9-rykiausi-rugsjo-albumai-23
85	https://emilijaviso.substack.com/p/bonus-ispudziai-is-varsuvos-22	BONUS: spdiai i Varuvos (22)	Titanikas! Avangardas! girl in red!	<html><head></head><body><p><em>Kadangi vl ivilkau save  spontanik solo kelion (<a href="https://emilijaviso.substack.com/p/muzikos-fursetas-17">apie ankstesn - ia</a>), ikart ir suraau kartus spdius. Didel j dalis visikai su muzika nesusij, bet Substack daug kas supranta kaip senamadik blog (kai dar nebuvo odio tinklaratis) ir rao tiesiog gyvenimikas impresijas, tai leisiu sau irgi taip suprast. Apie naujus lietuvikus albumus, kuri  mnes prisirinko visai nemaai, jau netrukus, kitoje AUSIES serijoje.</em></p><div><hr></div><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F19174be5-2e83-4e75-81fe-241fa2147bff_1836x4080.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F19174be5-2e83-4e75-81fe-241fa2147bff_1836x4080.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F19174be5-2e83-4e75-81fe-241fa2147bff_1836x4080.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F19174be5-2e83-4e75-81fe-241fa2147bff_1836x4080.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F19174be5-2e83-4e75-81fe-241fa2147bff_1836x4080.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F19174be5-2e83-4e75-81fe-241fa2147bff_1836x4080.jpeg" width="312" height="693.3333333333334" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/19174be5-2e83-4e75-81fe-241fa2147bff_1836x4080.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:4080,&quot;width&quot;:1836,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:312,&quot;bytes&quot;:2988276,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F19174be5-2e83-4e75-81fe-241fa2147bff_1836x4080.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F19174be5-2e83-4e75-81fe-241fa2147bff_1836x4080.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F19174be5-2e83-4e75-81fe-241fa2147bff_1836x4080.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F19174be5-2e83-4e75-81fe-241fa2147bff_1836x4080.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">Tekst pradeda ir ubaigia foto i lenkik tlik</figcaption></figure></div><p>Nesu didel keliautoja, kelionse ne tiek pailsiu, kiek padirbu (fizine prasme), paskui namie, komforto zonoj, turiu atsiilst. Bet iemet yra apms kakoks kelioni ias. Racionaliai suprantu, kad j skatina instagramai su kelioni foto ir iaip vyraujantis sitikinimas, kad prasmingam gyvenimui btina kuo daugiau keliaut. Bet kodl gi ne, itas ias man asmenikai naudingas, leidia save isibandyt, isikelt iki ir paskui bt patenkinta juos veikus.</p><p>Labai mgstu Varuv, man ji toks naujasis senasis Berlynas, nes dar ne tiek gentrifikuota ir iliaupsinta, visko joje yra, ir hipsteryn, ir smirdini skyli, ir muzikos parduotuvli, kur prasilenkdamas su pardavju turi upakaliais pasitrinti, ir pierogi su spirgais, ir egzotik pierogi, kuriuos turi su pagaliukais graibyt, ir aliojo tilto skulptr, ir puikaus drsaus modernaus meno, ir pritrenkiantis yd istorijos muziejus (POLIN), ir kaskart vis spdingiau atrodantis didel Stalino pimpal simbolizuojantis Paac Kultury i Nauki. O kur dar tas suvokimas, kad juk kone viskas,  k dabar iri, buvo sugriauta ir atstatyta.</p><div class="image-gallery-embed" data-attrs="{&quot;gallery&quot;:{&quot;images&quot;:[{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/18e9fda4-0d82-47b5-a5fe-ab63471af8c1_1836x3020.jpeg&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/c6789e67-1d1b-4bde-bf08-6d48cf17d370_3197x6538.jpeg&quot;}],&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;Nn, kaip patiems lenkams tas Stalino dangoraiis, bet man tai patinka.  Ir ilikusi 1912 m. eklektika&quot;,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;staticGalleryImage&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/8d6a34fc-5556-492e-8b2f-70a0e267be16_1456x720.png&quot;}},&quot;isEditorNode&quot;:true}"></div><p>Vaiavau spontanikai, nes autikas vos 30 eur  abi puses (labiau mgstu autikus, nes yra internetas, yra televizoriukai, yra kakavos). 1,5 dienos pabuvimui susiorganizavau ilg kultrin program, kuri, aiku, pranoko mano fizines jgas, tad paskutini konc jau tik vien ak atmerkus klausiau.</p><blockquote><h4>Wystawa TITANIC</h4></blockquote><p>Esu Titaniko fan nuo pat 1997 m., kai su mama Lietuvos kino teatre pairjau film. Paskui dar 4 kartus jau pati viena, vienuolikmet, irti to didingo ir aaringo reginio, dar kokius 10kart vliau liumbiau irdama per TV, tebeturiu stor papk su ikarpom i laikrai, nes anuomet niekas netingjo rayti apie DiCaprio ir apie populiariausi vis laik (iki tol) film.</p><p><a href="https://titanic.pl/">Parodos Varuvoje</a> (veiks iki met galo) atsiliepimai vidutiniki, manau, dl to, kad daug kas tikjosi parodos apie DiCaprio. Kiti gal man pamatysiantys iskirtin laivo prabang ir auksines suknias. Bet paroda rimta, tikjausi paskutins sals, skirtos reprezentacijai filmuose ir kt., bet net tokio pataikavimo nebuvo. Tik shope galima nusifotkint prie greenscreeno ir sigyt rakt pakabuk su Vandenyno irdim.</p><p>Ekspozicija atveta i Mokslo muziejaus Pitsburge (JAV), taigi joje daug dmesio technologijai ir mechanikai  kaip buvo statomas, kaip plauk, kaip skendo ir kaip dabar yra tyrinjamas ir 4 km gylyje aklinoje tamsoje damas gelevalgi mikroorganizm. Manoma, kad laivas galutinai subyrs per 4090 met, tad dar turim laiko  bei t itraukti, taiau paties Titaniko, deja, neitrauksim (taip kaip Vaz laivo Stokholme i XVI a.), nes dar toli grau iki tokio masto konservavimui reikaling technologij. Visi itraukti daikteliukai (daugiausia indai, taip pat paskiros detals  vairas, durys, elektros jungikliai, suoliuko rmas, papuoalai, cherubino skultrl, stovjusi prie garsij laipt) yra laikomi spec. slygomis.</p><div class="image-gallery-embed" data-attrs="{&quot;gallery&quot;:{&quot;images&quot;:[{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/2974e019-aab7-47cb-a78f-d2b24dafce6b_1836x2517.jpeg&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/122f8199-0ee6-4a3f-9209-1e83d385313f_1836x2632.jpeg&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/6947bee8-40a2-473f-beef-bcad4e4dd6b1_1836x2020.jpeg&quot;}],&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;Indai taip ir buvo sukrit Atlanto dugne&quot;,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;staticGalleryImage&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/e093631d-55ab-4f50-91a6-f90ab87b34ac_1456x474.png&quot;}},&quot;isEditorNode&quot;:true}"></div><p>Didiulje ekspozicijos teritorijoje tampi keleiviu (su bilietu, kuriame paminta konkretaus mogaus istorija), apeini III klass kajut, I klass laisvalaikio erdves (pirt), nusileidi prie didij katil, gauni paiupinti ledo luit. Prie kiekvieno daiktelio (neneiot puskojini)  ilgesn ar trumpesn konkretaus savininko istorija (matosi, kiek daug darbo  tokius tyrimus dta). Jei skirsite laiko viskam perskaityti, pasakojimas tikrai traukia ir sukelia jausm dl individuali tragedij (8 asmen eima turjo bilietus  kit laiv, bet buvo perkelti  ; visi nuskendo) ir dl socioistorini li, kuriuos Titanikas simbolizuoja: klasinio susiskirstymo (III klass keleiviams tokia kelion buvo spdingiausia gyvenimo patirtis), emigracijos svajoni, netiktinos prabangos (ir orios senj aristokrat laikysenos), netiktin besibaigianio aukso amiaus ambicij bei aklo pasitikjimo technologine paanga, ir viso to nugarmjimo  prat, prie pat prasidedant visai kitai, pasaulini kar, epochai.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fca80cf1a-88bc-4c75-a05d-2e0fff455af7_1836x2276.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fca80cf1a-88bc-4c75-a05d-2e0fff455af7_1836x2276.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fca80cf1a-88bc-4c75-a05d-2e0fff455af7_1836x2276.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fca80cf1a-88bc-4c75-a05d-2e0fff455af7_1836x2276.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fca80cf1a-88bc-4c75-a05d-2e0fff455af7_1836x2276.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fca80cf1a-88bc-4c75-a05d-2e0fff455af7_1836x2276.jpeg" width="426" height="528.0915032679738" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/ca80cf1a-88bc-4c75-a05d-2e0fff455af7_1836x2276.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:2276,&quot;width&quot;:1836,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:426,&quot;bytes&quot;:659234,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fca80cf1a-88bc-4c75-a05d-2e0fff455af7_1836x2276.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fca80cf1a-88bc-4c75-a05d-2e0fff455af7_1836x2276.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fca80cf1a-88bc-4c75-a05d-2e0fff455af7_1836x2276.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fca80cf1a-88bc-4c75-a05d-2e0fff455af7_1836x2276.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">III klass kajut </figcaption></figure></div><p>Jei domu, rekomenduoju labai linksm ir rimt brit podkast The Rest is History, kurio <a href="https://open.spotify.com/episode/0fMeR40Q8kEuCsmKXLWXr7?si=4866bff0b8cb4ae7">6 serijos skirtos Titanikui</a>, jo kontekstui, kelionei, keleiviams ir j likimams. Pavyzdiui, ar inojote, kad Titaniku plauk toks Charlesas Lightrolleris, kuriuo paremt persona Mr. Dawson Dunkirke vaidino Mark Rylance. Lightrolleris Titanike buvo antro rango pareignas, iki paskutins minuts padjo su evakuacija, keliskart skendo, galiausiai buvo nubloktas  vanden ir sikibs apvirtusios valties sulauk atplaukusios Carpathios. Pirmam pasauliniam kare jis vadovavo kariniam laivui, o Dunkirke, jau ijs  pensij, su snum savo asmenine jachta padjo igelbti 127 brit ir prancz karius.</p><div class="image-gallery-embed" data-attrs="{&quot;gallery&quot;:{&quot;images&quot;:[{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/f636e1a6-8c7b-44e7-bbc1-250a57ff8cbc_532x753.png&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/43c2da3e-87ec-4f99-a9a6-5eec588d2250_4976x5022.jpeg&quot;}],&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;staticGalleryImage&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/42355243-658f-4c08-a755-04902793597c_1456x720.png&quot;}},&quot;isEditorNode&quot;:true}"></div><p>Pabaigai tik priminsiu, kad 1912 m. dauguma laiv jau buvo pajgs veikti ledkaln  reikjo tiesiog j taranuoti, o ne sukti kairn.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F11111a92-ed1a-47ba-bfcc-758e94fd7f52_1836x2770.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F11111a92-ed1a-47ba-bfcc-758e94fd7f52_1836x2770.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F11111a92-ed1a-47ba-bfcc-758e94fd7f52_1836x2770.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F11111a92-ed1a-47ba-bfcc-758e94fd7f52_1836x2770.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F11111a92-ed1a-47ba-bfcc-758e94fd7f52_1836x2770.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F11111a92-ed1a-47ba-bfcc-758e94fd7f52_1836x2770.jpeg" width="380" height="573.3115468409586" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/11111a92-ed1a-47ba-bfcc-758e94fd7f52_1836x2770.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:2770,&quot;width&quot;:1836,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:380,&quot;bytes&quot;:2094676,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F11111a92-ed1a-47ba-bfcc-758e94fd7f52_1836x2770.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F11111a92-ed1a-47ba-bfcc-758e94fd7f52_1836x2770.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F11111a92-ed1a-47ba-bfcc-758e94fd7f52_1836x2770.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F11111a92-ed1a-47ba-bfcc-758e94fd7f52_1836x2770.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">Parodoj galima paliest ledo gabal</figcaption></figure></div><div><hr></div><blockquote><h4>Avant Art Festival </h4></blockquote><p>Du vakarus buvau trijuose Varuvos klubuose: Pardon, To Tu; Chmury ir Hydrogazadka. U ~30 eur iklausiau 7 labai skirting koncert. Nostalgikai prisiminiau prie 15 m. Lenk kultros namuose (Vilniuje) vykdavusius <a href="https://lt.wikipedia.org/wiki/A.LT">apdovanojimus A.LT</a>, kur vienoje scenoje pasirodydavo vis ne-pop stili muzikos atstovai. Varuvoje taip pat buvo domu stebti publik, atstovaujani visoms tebeegzistuojanios ir nykstanioms subkultroms, nuo sen reiveri iki jaun metalist, bei tiesiog paprastam visavalgiam mogui kaip a.</p><p>Taip pat galvojau apie tai, kad pas mus avangardas suprantama kaip kakas labai rimto, avangardin muzika skamba kokiam nors MC, Jaunos muzikos festivalyje ar bent jau Vilnius Jazz. Lenkikasis renginio konceptas buvo be jokio elitizmo, koncertai vyko toliau nuo centro, industriniuose klubuose/baruose/skylse. Klausytoj (ir atlikj) amius buvo tarp 20 ir 70 met.</p><p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QTskdzJ1VCE&amp;ab_channel=KEXP">MABE FRATTI</a> (Gvatemala/Meksika) trio grojo violonele paremt diaz su pop/folk elementais. Po io rimto, aukto lygio koncerto kiek komikai atrod <a href="https://youtu.be/NtCWDoYtExQ">P</a> (Pranczija/Gana)  labiau solo performansas nei muzika. Atlikja su zombio linzm vaikiojo tarp publikos ir prikidama arti veid gsdino vyrus (kakodl j publikoj buvo daugiau). Visgi saugi performanso riba nebuvo perengta, visi liko pakutenti, su nejaukiom ypsenlm, buvo daug k pafilmuoti, bet muzikinio ir idjinio turinio lyg ir nevelgiau. Nepaisant tarp meni atlikjai itatuiruoto smuiko rakto.</p><div class="native-video-embed" data-component-name="VideoPlaceholder" data-attrs="{&quot;mediaUploadId&quot;:&quot;48ba1398-c226-45fa-82be-198bb6a5a92b&quot;,&quot;duration&quot;:null}"></div><p>Dvi persipynusios grups i Brazilijos paliko didiausi spd. <a href="https://youtu.be/V6vwTQ3so_0">TEST</a>  vokalo/gitaros ir iauri bgn duetas grojo ekperimentin metal su grindcore / punk elementais. Turbt garsiausia ir labiausiai patyrusi festivalio grup <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZIRoS-woHvA&amp;ab_channel=Lovers%26Lollypops">DEAFKIDS</a> metal mai su elektronika, noizu ir poliritmine perkusija.</p><div class="native-video-embed" data-component-name="VideoPlaceholder" data-attrs="{&quot;mediaUploadId&quot;:&quot;ab655998-df5c-4307-9f65-c0f3626f5293&quot;,&quot;duration&quot;:null}"></div><p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ToaKh4aBVOA&amp;ab_channel=Taberculat">MASQUE NOIR</a> (Baltarusija/Lenkija) grojo free-improv diaz. Prie j vienam ilgam gabalui pasipras prisijung vietinis vokalistas, neblogai pasitaks ir parkavs. Pasirodo, grup propaguoja koncertus be jokio pasiruoimo atsitiktinse vietose su atsitiktiniais monmis.</p><div class="native-video-embed" data-component-name="VideoPlaceholder" data-attrs="{&quot;mediaUploadId&quot;:&quot;eaf2a59c-0513-49ef-8f84-d65f6cfdc572&quot;,&quot;duration&quot;:null}"></div><p>SEPERSA &amp; MATEUSZ KROL (Iranas/Lenkija) eksperimentavo su ritmo mainomis, bet atrod labiau besiavintys technologijom nei muzika. <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bfDHv3Mocjk&amp;t=1s&amp;ab_channel=obscuredbyears">Duetas MOE</a> (Norvegija) su nenusakomo amiaus ir stebtinos jgos seniuku Ikuro Takahashi (Japonija, perkusija) iek tiek primin Bjork su politikais paklykavimais ir pasiraitymais tarp publikos. Bosin gitara dundjo nuostabiai. Pabaigoje vokalist sak: Ai, kad leidiate groti avangard.</p><div class="native-video-embed" data-component-name="VideoPlaceholder" data-attrs="{&quot;mediaUploadId&quot;:&quot;f9d3b8f9-5c9f-4dc2-844d-b64347d434c3&quot;,&quot;duration&quot;:null}"></div><p>(Prie grupi pavadinim pridedu geresni nuorodas  geresnius video nei itie mano pigiu telefonu filmuoti.) </p><p>iaip ko pasigedau, tai tik lenk (ant scenos). Bet, kiek suprantu, organizatoriai lenkus labiau promina usienyje, o  festival daugiau vea usienieius. Mums palinkiau daugiau toki tarpini erdvi/ rengini  tarp elitini sali ir pogrindini skyli. Ir kad alaus kainos bt labiau kaip Lenkijoj, o ne kaip vedijoj.</p><div><hr></div><blockquote><h4>girl in red</h4></blockquote><p>Dar, kad maa nepasirodyt, apsilankiau popmuzikos koncerte. 25-eri Marie Ulven i Norvegijos igarsjo 2018 m. su singlu I wanna be your girlfriend, dabar jis perklausom nusileidia vir milijardo kart perklausytai dainai we fell in love in october. 2021 m. debiutinis albumas buvo labai skmingas, antrasis, pasirods iemet, jau maiau.</p><p>Nedidel sporto hal buvo iparduota (biliet pirkau u 40eur). 90 procent publikos sudar jaunuts neheteronormatyvikai atrodanios merginos (Marie - lesbiet, apie tai i dalies ir jos dainos) su iurpiai trumpais sijonliais, plytom pdkelnm, apsmukusiom kelnm, gotiku makiau ir kit stili elementais. Koncerte buvo galima sitikinti tiesa, kad gamtoje nra garsiau klykianio gyvno u paaugl mergait. Stereotipikai atrodantys vyrai ia buvo nebent tiai arba apsauginiai. Tikrai keistas pojtis bti minioj, kurioj visi ne auktesni u mane.</p><p>Marie sirgo, sak: iandien dar su niekuo nekalbjau, saugojau bals, js pirmi, tai girdsit daug nesmoni. Atliko Billie Eilish dainos fragment su odiais <em>miau miau miaaauu</em>. Vien krin dedikavo lenkikai virtuvei. O savo avinga laisva laikysena scenoje primin msik Beatrich ar maut miel Courtney Love. Buvo atliktas ir publikos praskyrimo stebuklas (r. klip), kai Marie atsiduria minios epicentre. Garso kokyb, deja, buvo lenkika, o gal tiesiog mano ausys jau per senos itiems daniams.</p><div id="youtube2-w9RTuUTl-40" class="youtube-wrap" data-attrs="{&quot;videoId&quot;:&quot;w9RTuUTl-40&quot;,&quot;startTime&quot;:null,&quot;endTime&quot;:null}" data-component-name="Youtube2ToDOM"><div class="youtube-inner"><iframe src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/w9RTuUTl-40?rel=0&amp;autoplay=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;enablejsapi=0" frameborder="0" loading="lazy" gesture="media" allow="autoplay; fullscreen" allowautoplay="true" allowfullscreen="true" width="728" height="409"></iframe></div></div><div><hr></div><p>Tiek spdi i Varuvos. Raginu ten vaiuoti, pasijusit kaip ponai (finansine prasme). Pastaraisiais metais su lenk kultra jauiu vis didesn bendrum, pradjau galvoti, kad vertt jau vaduotis i istorini traum ir pastebt, kas mus sieja. Daug kuo esam pranaesni, progresyvesni (pvz., kasdienybs technologijom: netgi Varuvoj ne visur gali susimokt kortele, kai pas mus jau grynais ne visur priima; be to, lenkai labai rko senovikas cigaretes, kai pas mus seniausiai visi veipina), be to, turim geresn estetin skon. Tad nereikia jaustis kaip kokiam dikio nuskriaustam vaikui.</p><div><hr></div><p><em>Kadangi mons nepaliauja man silyti pinig, tai padariau jums toki galimyb. U tekst padkoti ir prie mano gerovs prisidti galite paspaud mygtuk emiau ir ved savo sugalvot sum. Taiau esat laisvi to ir nedaryti. Ai.</em></p><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://buy.stripe.com/4gw7tv5Tj63OfGUdQR&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Prisidti&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"><a class="button primary" href="https://buy.stripe.com/4gw7tv5Tj63OfGUdQR"><span>Prisidti</span></a></p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb971639e-6a68-4f72-88ac-2d1baf1283c6_4080x1836.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb971639e-6a68-4f72-88ac-2d1baf1283c6_4080x1836.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb971639e-6a68-4f72-88ac-2d1baf1283c6_4080x1836.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb971639e-6a68-4f72-88ac-2d1baf1283c6_4080x1836.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb971639e-6a68-4f72-88ac-2d1baf1283c6_4080x1836.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb971639e-6a68-4f72-88ac-2d1baf1283c6_4080x1836.jpeg" width="334" height="742.3241758241758" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/b971639e-6a68-4f72-88ac-2d1baf1283c6_4080x1836.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:3236,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;